ched%20your%20lives%20and%20I%20could%20not%20be%20more%20grateful%20to%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20you%20for%20being%20brave%20enough%20to%20share%20your%20experiences.%20To%20all%20our%20wonderful%2C%20loving%2C%20amazing%2C%20and%20brave%20heroes%20there%20is%20so%20much%20I%20want%20to%20say%2C%20and%20so%20much%20gratitude%20I%20want%20to%20express%20to%20you%20all%20for%20letting%20me%20into%20your%20homes%20and%20hearts.%20It's%20all%20because%20of%20you%20that%20I've%20kept%20going%20all%20these%20years%20and%20each%20and%20every%20one%20of%20you%20have%20changed%20me%20for%20the%20better.%20I'm%20so%20very%20proud%20of%20all%20of%20you!%20Being%20able%20to%20help%20guide%20you%20to%20find%20the%20best%20version%20of%20yourselves%20is%20something%20I%20never%20took%20for%20granted%20and%20never%20will.%20It's%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%20that%20I%20announce%20that%20season%208%20will%20be%20my%20final%20season%20on%20Queer%20Eye.%20It's%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20decision%20to%20be%20at%20peace%20with%2C%20but%20a%20necessary%20one.%20Although%20my%20journey%20with%20Queer%20Eye%20is%20over%2C%20my%20journey%20with%20you%20is%20not.%20You%20will%20be%20seeing%20more%20of%20me%20very%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20after%20Berk's%20exit%20was%20announced%2C%20a%20source%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fbobby-berk-remains-amicable-queer-eye-castmates-source-exclusive-8401989%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E%20magazine%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20parting%20was%20amicable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBobby's%20departure%20is%20unrelated%20to%20relationships%20with%20his%20castmates%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20the%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20statement%20was%20contradicted%20by%20a%20source%20who%20told%20Us%20Weekly%20that%20Berk%20was%20%26quot%3Basked%20to%20leave%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20tension%20with%20the%20cast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20many%20challenges%20with%20scheduling%20%5Band%5D%20there%20was%20a%20loss%20of%20interest%20from%20Bobby%20filming%20the%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binsider%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usmagazine.com%2Fentertainment%2Fnews%2Fbobby-berk-left-queer-eye-after-challenges-with-cast-and-schedule%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUs%20Weekly%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20network%20and%20the%20cast%20thought%20it%20was%20time%20to%20bring%20in%20fresh%20blood.%20His%20heart%20was%20not%20in%20it%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cast%20started%20to%20resent%20him%20because%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202024%3A%20Netflix%20announces%20interior%20designer%20Jeremiah%20Brent%20as%20Berk's%20replacement%20for%20season%209%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222235%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeremiah%20Brent%20is%20seen%20at%20Jeremiah%20Brent's%20book%20%26quot%3BThe%20Space%20That%20Keeps%20You%26quot%3B%20launch%20party%20hosted%20by%20Brian%20and%20Tracy%20Robbins%20on%20March%202%2C%202024%20in%20Montecito%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb521cce7f1785b2e7f185%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221676%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeremiah%20Brent%20is%20replacing%20Bobby%20Berk.%3Cp%3EEric%20Charbonneau%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Paramount%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftudum%2Farticles%2Fqueer-eye-season-9-jeremiah-brent%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrent%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20his%20start%20as%20celebrity%20stylist%20Rachel%20Zoe's%20styling%20associate%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Rachel%20Zoe%20Project%26quot%3B%20in%202011.%20He's%20also%20been%20married%20to%20famous%20interior%20designer%20Nate%20Berkus%20since%202014%20and%20they%20have%20two%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Brent's%20hiring%2C%20Netflix%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22htt