ply%2C%20lots%20of%20options%20for%20short%20manicures%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Adhesive%20system%20doesn't%20last%20as%20long%20as%20glue%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImpress%20nails%20don't%20come%20with%20glue%2C%20so%20these%20are%20perfect%20for%20the%20person%20who%20is%20new%20to%20press-on%20nails%20and%20scared%20of%20commitment.%20The%20pressure-sensitive%20adhesive%20is%20already%20attached%20to%20the%20nail%20which%20makes%20it%20super%20easy%20to%20apply%2C%20and%20I%20found%20that%20the%20Impress%20adhesive%20is%20much%20stronger%20than%20the%20adhesives%20that%20come%20with%20brands%20that%20offer%20glue%20as%20well.%20Also%2C%20I%20noticed%20Impress%20has%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20designs%20for%20short%20nail%20manicures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20classic%20styles%3A%20Static%20Nails%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wearing%20Static%20Nails%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f9a6660729770012b953ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShayla%20Martin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20comes%20in%20the%20box%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2024%20nails%20in%2012%20sizes%2C%20Static%20Nails'%20non-damaging%20glue%2C%20instructions%2C%20buffer%2C%20and%20a%20nail%20file.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20the%20brand%20said%20they'd%20last%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E7-18%20days%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20they%20actually%20lasted%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E5%20days%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGreat%20for%20French%20manicures%20and%20unfussy%20designs%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EInstructions%20a%20little%20misleading%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStatic%20Nails%20are%20reusable%20pop-on%20manicures%20in%20five%20shapes%3A%20round%2C%20coffin%2C%20square%2C%20almond%2C%20and%20stiletto%20and%20are%20known%20for%20their%20approachable%20styles%20in%20solid%20colors%20and%20multi-colored%20French%20manis.%20Static%20also%20comes%20with%20light%20pink%20glue%2C%20which%20was%20helpful%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20the%20directions%20called%20for%20too%20much%20nail%20glue.%20I%20followed%20the%20directions%2C%20which%20said%20to%20apply%20a%20thin%20layer%20of%20glue%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20Static%20Nail%20and%20then%20a%20%26quot%3Bgenerous%26quot%3B%20layer%20of%20glue%20to%20the%20natural%20nail%2C%20but%20I%20ended%20up%20with%20glue%20all%20over%20the%20place%20and%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20nail%20which%20damaged%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELargest%20variety%3A%20The%20Nailest%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waring%20The%20Nailest%20nails%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f9acea0729770012b9563b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShayla%20Martin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20comes%20in%20the%20box%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2030%20nails%2C%2028%20adhesive%20tabs%2C%20nail%20glue%2C%20mini%20file%2C%20and%20a%20cuticle%20push%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20the%20brand%20said%20they'd%20last%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E1%20to%202%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20they%20actually%20lasted%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%205%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBig%20selection%20of%20shapes%20and%20designs%2C%20thicker%20than%20other%20brands%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20reviewers%20say%20that%20they%20run%20small%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nailest%20has%20the%20largest%20variety%20of%20nails%20of%20all%20the%20brands%20I%20tested.%20Of%20their%20instant%20acrylic%20sets%20(read-to-ship)%20they%20have%20pretty%20much%20any%20shape%2C%20length%2C%20color%2C%20and%20finish%20you%20can%20imagine%2C%20and%20they%20also%20offer%20handcrafted%20sets%20painted%20with%20at%20least%205%20layers%20of%20gel%20polish.%20They're%20thicker%20quality%20and%20way%20sturdier%20than%20most%20press-on%20nails.%20As%20with%20other%20brands%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20not%20following%20the%20directions%20to%20apply%20glue%20on%20the%20faux%20and%20natural%20nails%20because%20it%20results%20in%20excess%20glue%2C%20making%20the%20nails%20messy%2Fsticky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20with%20crystals%3A%20Marmalade%20Nails%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wearing%20Marmalade%20Nails%20in%20Aria%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f9a505fc253600181fdb9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShayla%20Martin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20comes%20in%20the%20box%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2024%20press-on%20nails%20in%2012%20sizes%2C%20a%20nail%20file%2C%20nail%20glue%2C%20manicure%20stick%2C%20nail%20removal%20tool%2C%20and%20application%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20the%20brand%20said%20they'd%20last%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E11-14%20days%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20they%20actually%20lasted%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E6%20days%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELots%20of%20variety%20in%20shapes%2C%20designs%2C%20and%20crystals%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECertain%20styles%20may%20discolor%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Aria%20is%20a%20short%2C%20matte%2C%20square%20white%20mani%20with%20a%20sparkly%20accent%20nail%20of%20Swarovski%20crystals%2C%20which%20make%20them%20perfect%20for%20summer%2C%20but%20I%20noticed%20that%20the%20white%20nails%20became%20discolored%20to%20a%20light%20brown%20over%20time.%20So%2C%20while%20you%20may%20want%20to%20skip%20the%20Aria%20style%2C%20I%20think%20Marmalade%20has%20some%20of%20the%20most%20creative%20and%20dramatic%20styles%20(I've%20got%20my%20eye%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarmaladenails.com%2Fcollections%2Fnails%2Fproducts%2Fmosaic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMosaic%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarmaladenails.com%2Fcollections%2Fnails%2Fproducts%2Fice-queen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIce%20Queen%3C%2Fa%3E).%20I%20also%20like%20the%20light%20pink%20nail%20glue%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20gauge%20how%20much%20glue%20you're%20applying.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20glue%20did%20feel%20stronger%20than%20most%2C%20and%20I%20damaged%20one%20of%20my%20natural%20nails%20when%20removing%20the%20press-ons%2C%20so%20take%20caution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20unique%20designs%3A%20Clutch%20Nails%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wearing%20Lucky%20Clutch%20Nails%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f9a7190729770012b953f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShayla%20Martin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20comes%20in%20the%20box%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2024%20nails%2C%20file%2C%20and%20nail%20glue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20the%20brand%20said%20they'd%20last%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E7-14%20days%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20they%20actually%20lasted%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E4%20days.%20One%20came%20off%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20but%20I%20reglued%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Lots%20of%20fun%20designs%2C%20mostly%20water-resistant%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20May%20not%20last%20as%20long%20as%20others%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClutch%20Nails%20styles%20are%20so%20fun%2C%20there's%20really%20no%20other%20way%20to%20describe%20them.%20Expect%20bright%20colors%2C%20designs%2C%20and%20prints%20(checker%2C%20flames%2C%20stars%2C%20etc.)%2C%20holiday%20themes%2C%20and%20varying%20lengths.%20I%20have%20to%20admit%20that%20when%20I%20tested%20these%20nails%2C%20I%20spent%20nearly%20all%20day%20at%20the%20pool%20about%20an%20hour%20after%20applying%20them%20but%20they%20held%20on%20really%20well%20in%20so%20much%20water.%20These%20came%20with%20light%20pink%20nail%20glue%20as%20well%2C%20which%20I've%20non-scientifically%20decided%20is%20stronger%20than%20the%20clear%20glue%2C%20so%20I%20assume%20they%20would%20have%20lasted%20longer%20had%20I%20not%20been%20in%20the%20pool%20all%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%3Cp%3EAfter%20perusing%20both%20my%20local%20drugstore%20and%20Instagram%2C%20I%20tested%20nine%20different%20brands%20of%20nails%20and%20chose%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20set%20based%20on%20how%20long%20they%20lasted.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20other%20boundaries%20I%20applied%20with%20each%20test%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20a%20nail%20came%20off%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20application%2C%20I%20gave%20it%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20doubt%20and%20assumed%20there%20was%20a%20human%20error%20on%20my%20part%2C%20glued%20it%20back%20on%2C%20and%20waited%20until%20another%20nail%20fell%20off%20later.%20Once%20multiple%20nails%20started%20to%20disappear%2C%20I%20ended%20its%20test%20and%20moved%20to%20the%20next%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20only%20used%20the%20nail%20glue%20that%20the%20nails%20came%20with.%20However%2C%20several%20friends%20told%20me%20that%20if%20you%20REALLY%20want%20your%20nails%20to%20last%2C%20it's%20better%20to%20buy%20nail%20glue%20from%20a%20beauty%20supply%20store%20or%20Amazon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20the%20set%20came%20with%20both%20adhesive%20and%20glue%2C%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20test%2C%20I%20used%20the%20glue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20always%20washed%20my%20hands%20thoroughly%20before%20applying%20and%20if%20the%20set%20came%20with%20alcohol%20wipes%20(most%20do)