ener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dea2046da5010a1bb8754ab0a6e531f74a8b7b435d30bd3fed2ecb254a6a4df94%26postID%3D65eb290048eec3d3e78200cc%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fvizio-quantum-pro-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0C6XSWTYC%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHisense%20U7K%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3De2f89dc87589dd740fdb72391cf0ec7fbc9181bda9a59ce2b6aabcb3cd9009c2%26postID%3D65eb290048eec3d3e78200cc%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fvizio-quantum-pro-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0C1J4XCCL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETCL%20Q7%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20impactful.%20On%20the%20streaming%20front%2C%20Vizio's%20interface%20has%20improved%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20as%20adaptable%20as%20the%20systems%20that%20drive%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-tv%5C%22%3Ebest%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Quantum%20Pro%20has%20its%20advantages%2C%20including%20impressive%20off-axis%20viewing%20and%20competitive%20gaming%20and%20motion%20response%20via%20its%20120Hz%20panel.%20That%20could%20make%20it%20a%20viable%20option%20for%20those%20with%20larger%20spaces%20who%20watch%20a%20lot%20of%20TV%20in%20bright%20lighting.%20But%20otherwise%2C%20the%20competition%20is%20stacked%20against%20the%20Quantum%20Pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Setup%20and%20design%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Quantum%20Pro%20is%20simple%20to%20set%20up%20and%20looks%20good%20on%20the%20mantle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holding%20a%20Vizio%20remote%20with%20a%20Vizio%20TV%20out%20of%20focus%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb313690413ab8e1dab65b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Quantum%20Pro%20has%20a%20simplified%20remote%20with%20built-in%20voice%20control.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20the%20Quantum%20Pro%20from%20the%20box%20to%20your%20TV%20console%20is%20relatively%20simple.%20The%20twin%20stands%20offer%20dual%20positions%2C%20letting%20you%20raise%20the%20TV%20a%20few%20inches%20to%20leave%20room%20for%20a%20moderately%20thin%20soundbar.%20One%20point%20to%20note%3A%20The%20stands%20push%20out%20pretty%20far%20to%20each%20side%20(around%2050%20inches%20apart%20in%20the%2065-inch%20model%20we%20reviewed)%2C%20so%20those%20with%20smaller%20consoles%20may%20need%20to%20mount%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20matte%20plastic%20at%20the%20backside%20is%20unremarkable%2C%20but%20the%20TV's%20thin%20black%20bezels%20up%20front%20offer%20a%20classy%2C%20if%20understated%2C%20aesthetic.%20An%20accessible%20inputs%20cubby%20at%20the%20right%20side%20lets%20you%20quickly%20connect%20your%20components%2C%20and%20once%20you've%20powered%20the%20TV%20on%2C%20it%20recognizes%20your%20devices%20and%20sends%20you%20through%20an%20intuitive%20startup%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20manual%20password%20entry%2C%20the%20TV%20will%20give%20you%20a%20QR%20code%20for%20its%20mobile%20app%2C%20but%20that's%20mostly%20just%20a%20secondary%20remote.%20Most%20of%20the%20setup%20process%20happens%20with%20the%20ergonomic%2C%20Roku-esque%20remote.%20Still%2C%20Vizio%20makes%20the%20process%20graciously%20painless%2C%20assisting%20you%20in%20selecting%20your%20favorite%20apps%2C%20and%20even%20cueing%20up%20settings%20like%20turning%20off%20the%20eco%20mode%2C%20which%20helps%20keep%20performance%20consistent%20(and%20is%20surprisingly%20confusing%20to%20find%20in%20some%20TVs).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVizio%20conveniently%20gathers%20all%20major%20settings%20into%20one%20accessible%20window%2C%20available%20with%20a%20tap%20of%20the%20settings%20key.%20From%20there%2C%20you%20can%20do%20everything%20from%20adjusting%20game%20settings%20and%20picture%20modes%20to%20pairing%20your%20Bluetooth%20headphones%20without%20digging%20through%20multiple%20menus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20performance%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20picture%20is%20bright%20from%20any%20angle%20but%20struggles%20in%20the%20dark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Vizio%20Quantum%20Pro%20TV%20displaying%20a%20scene%20from%20%26quot%3BGuardians%20of%20the%20Galaxy%20Vol.%202%26quot%3B%20on%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb31d6ce7f1785b2e7cb9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV%20offers%20good%20HDR%20performance%20with%20bright%20highlights%2C%20but%20black%20levels%20are%20sometimes%20elevated.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Quantum%20Pro's%20specifications%20are%20solid%20for%20a%20midrange%20QLED.%20It%20boasts%20quantum%20dots%20to%20produce%20a%20wide%20color%20gamut%20and%20full-array%20local%20dimming%20to%20control%20its%20light%20output.%20But%2C%20unlike%20the%20competing%20Hisense%20U7K%2C%20the%20TV%20uses%20regular%20LEDs%20rather%20than%20Mini%20LEDs%2C%20and%20its%20number%20of%20dimming%20zones%20is%20small.%20This%20leads%20to%20some%20performance%20quirks%20depending%20on%20your%20viewing%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrow%20on%20some%20flashy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-4k%5C%22%3E4K%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20video%20in%20a%20reasonably%20well-lit%20room%2C%20and%20the%20Quantum%20Pro's%20picture%20looks%20punchy%20and%20well-balanced%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Calibrated%20mode%20we%20used%20for%20most%20of%20our%20testing.%20The%20screen%20is%20relatively%20clear%20with%20good%20uniformity%2C%20so%20you%20won't%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20dingy%20columns%20or%20artifacts%20during%20a%20hockey%20or%20football%20game.%20With%20peak%20brightness%20pushing%20toward%201%2C000%20nits%2C%20the%20image%20looks%20flashy%20enough%20to%20showcase%20both%20regular%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%3EHDR%3C%2Fa%3E%20content%2C%20and%20the%20quantum%20dot%20colors%20are%20full%2C%20if%20not%20always%20natural.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20put%20the%20Quantum%20Pro%20under%20a%20closer%20lens%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20and%20it%20starts%20to%20reveal%20some%20of%20its%20more%20obvious%20shortcomings.%20The%20TV%20does%20an%20OK%20job%20with%20most%20HD%20content%20from%20sources%20like%20a%20Blu-ray%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-hdtv-indoor-antenna%5C%22%3EHD%20antenna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20to%20have%20trouble%20upscaling%20streaming%20content.%20We%20didn't%20expect%20a%201080p%20stream%20of%20%26quot%3BDune%26quot%3B%20to%20look%20amazing%20(thanks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-much-is-hulu%5C%22%3EHulu%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20but%20it%20looked%20particularly%20noisy%20and%20almost%20abstract%20in%20some%20scenes%20with%20the%20Quantum%20Pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20notably%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20convincing%20black%20levels%20keeps%20the%20Pro%20from%20creating%20the%20kind%20of%20rich%20and%20immersive%20contrast%20offered%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-4k-tv%5C%22%3Ebest%204K%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20class.%20Vizio's%20local%20dimming%20is%20particularly%20underpowered%20here%2C%20clumsily%20spilling%20the%20backlight%20around%20bright%20images%20on%20dark%20backdrops%2C%20even%20affecting%20letterbox%20lines%20during%20films%20like%20the%20final%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20sequel.%20Moving%20the%20Active%20Full%20Array%20setting%20to%20%26quot%3BLow%26quot%3B%20reduces%20the%20effect%20but%20comes%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20overall%20brightness.%20When%20stacking%20the%20Quantum%20Pro%20against%20the%20rich%20black%20levels%20and%20pinpoint%20local%20dimming%20of%20our%20favorites%20like%20the%20Hisense%20U7K%2C%20there's%20just%20no%20comparison.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReviewers%20tend%20to%20emphasize%20black%20levels%20a%20lot%20because%20the%20darker%20the%20backdrop%2C%20the%20better%20a%20TV's%20other%20elements%20can%20shine%20(literally)%20for%20a%20more%20compelling%20picture.%20It's%20a%20big%20reason%20why%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-oled-tv%5C%22%3Ebest%20OLED%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20their%20perfect%20black%20levels%2C%20are%20so%20beloved.%20And%20it's%20why%20Hisense%2C%20TCL%2C%20and%20premium%20brands%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-samsung-tvs%5C%22%3ESamsung%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Sony%20load%20up%20many%20dimming%20zones%20and%20use%20Mini%20LED%20backlights%20for%20fine-tuned%20contrast%20control%20in%20their%20top%20QLED%20TVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20area%20in%20which%20most%20QLED%20TVs%20generally%20struggle%20is%20off-axis%20viewing%2C%20and%20this%20is%20somewhere%20that%20the%20Quantum%20Pro%20actually%20has%20a%20leg%20up.%20Typically%2C%20moving%20off%20to%20a%20display's%20side%20even%20a%20few%20feet%20(especially%20with%20value-forward%20TVs)%20significantly%20reduces%20color%20vibrancy%20and%20contrast.%20Likely%20due%20to%20Vizio's%20use%20of%20an%20IPS%20(or%20similar)%20panel%20style%2C%20the%20Quantum%20Pro%20easily%20outdoes%20its%20main%20rivals%20there%2C%20even%20matching%20up%20well%20with%20some%20of%20the%20best%20QLED%20TVs%20on%20the%20market%2C%20like%20Samsung's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3De7c464865dc5819a1e35b3e74a4d991230346bf977335943cdb8b7ec1ae8c2e1%26postID%3D65eb290048eec3d3e78200cc%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fvizio-quantum-pro-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSAMSUNG-Tracking-Anti-Glare-Q-Symphony-QN65QN90C%252Fdp%252FB0BTTWV394%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQN90C%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Quantum%20Pro's%20120Hz%20refresh%20rate%20also%20does%20a%20fine%20job%20with%20fast-moving%20content%20like%20sports%2C%20while%20adding%20a%20bit%20of%20motion%20interpolation%20in%20the%20settings%20helps%20it%20avoid%20jerky%20stuttering%20and%20motion%20artifacts%20that%20can%20pop%20up%20during%20tricky%20camera%20movements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20OS%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVizio's%20smart%20interface%20is%20simple%20but%20bloated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222266%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Vizio%20smart%20TV%20hanging%20on%20wall%20while%20displaying%20the%20Home%20screen%20menu.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb5188ce7f1785b2e7f102%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVizio's%20smart%20TV%20operating%20system%20works%20well%20enough%20despite%20a%20few%20shortcomings.%3Cp%3EVizio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVizio's%20smart%20interface%2C%20which%20was%20rebranded%20from%20SmartCast%20to%20Home%20Screen%20(AKA%20Home)%2C%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20since%20the%20days%20when%20you%20had%20to%20%26quot%3Bcast%26quot%3B%20most%20of%20your%20content%20to%20the%20TV%20from%20a%20mobile%20device.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Vizio%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20ship%20some%20TVs%20with%20an%20Android%20tablet%20purpose-built%20for%20the%20task%2C%20with%20only%20a%20few%20built-in%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20the%20interface%20looks%20a%20lot%20more%20like%20most%20competitors.%20You'll%20find%20conveniences%20like%20%26quot%3BTrending%20Now%26quot%3B%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%2C%20easy%20access%20to%20all%20your%20connected%20devices%2C%20and%20a%20handy%20voice%20search%20feature%20via%20the%20remote's%20mic%20key.%20The%20layout%20of%20tabs%20and%20tiles%20is%20especially%20reminiscent%20of%20Google%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20fitting%20since%20that's%20become%20the%20go-to%20smart%20system%20for%20many%20top%20Vizio%20competitors%2C%20including%20TCL%2C%20Hisense%2C%20and%20even%20Sony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20difference%2C%20and%20what%20became%20most%20frustrating%20after%20days%20of%20use%2C%20is%20the%20constant%20pushing%20of%20Vizio's%20Watch%20Free%2B%20TV%20service.%20This%20is%20far%20from%20unique%20to%20Vizio%2C%20but%20what%20stands%20out%20here%20is%20just%20how%20many%20utterly%20forgotten%20TV%20shows%20and%20movies%20pop%20up.%20The%20homepage's%20largest%20slice%20of%20on-screen%20real%20estate%20entices%20you%20daily%20with%20hot%20titles%20like%202005's%20%26quot%3BBewitched%26quot%3B%20reboot%20or%202008's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Accidental%20Husband.%26quot%3B%20The%20app%20bar%20is%20similarly%20loaded%20with%20stuff%20you%20don't%20want%2C%20though%20you%20can%20rearrange%20the%20order%20and%20drop%20some%20(though%20not%20all)%20of%20the%20bloat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20other%20TV%20systems%2C%20there's%20no%20built-in%20access%20to%20Alexa%20or%20Google%20Assistant%2C%20so%20you'll%20need%20a%20secondary%20device%20to%20use%20them.%20There's%20also%20no%20apparent%20way%20to%20access%20shows%20and%20movies%20in%20progress%20from%20the%20main%20screen.%20This%20is%20a%20convenience%20that%20other%20smart%20TV%20platforms%20offer%20to%20save%20you%20from%20having%20to%20dive%20back%20into%20each%20individual%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20has%20its%20benefits%2C%20starting%20with%20a%20settings%20system%20that's%20more%20accessible%20and%20less%20cluttered%20than%20competitors%20like%20Samsung's%20Tizen%20system.%20Its%20performance%20is%20also%20remarkably%20smooth%20and%20fluid%2C%20which%20isn't%20always%20the%20case%20with%20the%20competition.%20Google%20TV%20tends%20to%20be%20especially%20laggy%20in%20some%20midrange%20models.%20As%20before%2C%20you%20can%20cast%20content%20via%20AirPlay%20and%20Chromecast.%20All%20told%2C%20Home%20does%20enough%20to%20be%20your%20daily%20driver%2C%20but%20you%20may%20want%20to%20browse%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-streaming-devices%5C%22%3Ebest%20streaming%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20you%20want%20to%20try%20another%20interface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Gaming%20features%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20TV%20offers%20good%20gaming%20features%20(with%20some%20caveats)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Vizio%20TV%20showing%20its%20gaming%20signal%20menu%20while%20playing%20God%20of%20Ward%20on%20the%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb338a90413ab8e1dab7fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Quantum%20Pro%20doesn't%20have%20a%20pop-up%20gaming%20bar%2C%20but%20you%20can%20access%20gaming%20settings%20through%20the%20main%20menu.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGaming%20with%20the%20Quantum%20Pro%20is%20mostly%20a%20good%20time%2C%20especially%20for%20brighter%20titles%20like%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgod-of-war-ragnarok-review%5C%22%3EGod%20of%20War%3A%20Ragnarok%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20As%20expected%2C%20when%20paired%20with%20a%20modern%20console%20like%20the%20PS5%2C%20the%20TV%20jumps%20straight%20into%20game%20mode%20to%20reduce%20input%20lag%20thanks%20to%20ALLM%20(Auto%20Low%20Latency%20Mode)%2C%20and%20it%20offers%20multiple%20flavors%20of%20VRR%20(Variable%20Refresh%20Rate)%20for%20tear-free%20PC%20and%20console%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20drawbacks%20worth%20noting%20for%20more%20avid%20gamers.%20While%20Viz