20extra%20features%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fsleepmapper%2Fid1258577276%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPhilips%20SleepMapper%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20used%20this%20model%2C%20like%20the%20sleep-environment%20monitoring%20and%20extended%20customization.%20I%20hope%20Philips%20comes%20out%20with%20a%20new%20sunrise%20alarm%20clock%20that%20features%20all%20of%20the%20Philips%20SmartSleep%20Connected%20options%20but%20is%20shaped%20like%20this%20model%20to%20simulate%20that%20beautiful%2C%20natural%20sunrise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fphilips-smart-sleep-wake-up-light-review%5C%22%3EPhilips%20SmartSleep%20Wake-Up%20Light%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20personalization%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20personalization%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hatch%20Restore%202%20is%20the%20latest%20version%20of%20the%20popular%2C%20customizable%20sunrise%20alarm%20clock.%20We%20liked%20the%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhatch-restore-sunrise-alarm-clock-review%5C%22%3EHatch%20Restore%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20its%20many%20light%20and%20sound%20options.%20The%20latest%20model%20has%20some%20small%20improvements.%20It%20usually%20retails%20for%20around%20%24200%2C%20about%20%2470%20more%20than%20the%20older%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20noticeable%20difference%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bsleep%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Brise%26quot%3B%20buttons.%20You%20can%20tap%20either%20to%20start%20the%20programs%20you%20set%20up%20in%20the%20app%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fhatch-sleep%2Fid1158048301%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.hatchbaby.rest%26hl%3Den_US%26gl%3DUS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Do%20a%20short%20press%20of%20either%20button%20to%20snooze.%20Hold%20down%20the%20button%2C%20and%20it%20shuts%20the%20routine%20off.%20The%20older%20model%20had%20a%20single%20button%20that%20was%20much%20smaller%2C%20which%20I%20had%20to%20fumble%20around%20for%20some%20mornings%20to%20turn%20the%20alarm%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20original%20Restore%20had%20a%20single%20speaker%2C%20the%20newest%20one%20has%20three%2C%20helping%20fill%20out%20the%20sleep%20and%20wake%20sounds.%20The%20entire%20front%20is%20covered%20in%20a%20linen%20fabric%2C%20available%20in%20three%20colors%20(brown%2C%20cream%2C%20and%20gray).%20This%20gives%20the%20Restore%202%20a%20more%20refined%20look%20and%20helps%20diffuse%20the%20light%20more%20than%20the%20original's%20plastic%20front.%20The%20half-oval%20shape%20is%20similar%20and%20mimics%20a%20sun%20rising%20over%20the%20horizon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hatch%20Restore%202%20glows%20reddish%20and%20displays%2011%3A20%20on%20a%20bedside%20table%20next%20to%20a%20lamp%20and%20book.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6410817e6966eb001957c358%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hatch%20Restore%202%20has%20the%20most%20personalization%20options%2C%20from%20a%20rainbow%20of%20colors%20for%20display%20to%20many%20sleep%20sounds.%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20app%2C%20you'll%20find%20sleep%20sounds%20ranging%20from%20pink%20noise%20to%20owl%20calls.%20You%20can%20set%20the%20duration%20and%20volume%20or%20have%20it%20run%20until%20you%20tap%20the%20clock's%20button.%20If%20you%20prefer%20to%20fall%20asleep%20to%20waves%20but%20want%20constant%20white%20noise%20while%20you%20sleep%2C%20you%20can%20set%20that%20up%2C%20too.%20You%20can%20choose%20from%2013%20wake-up%20sounds%20for%20mornings%20and%20pick%20a%20lighting%20color%20and%20brightness%20level.%20You%20can%20select%20the%20alarm%20duration%20and%20when%20you%20want%20to%20set%20the%20device%20to%20start%20gradually%20brightening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20get%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20functionality%20from%20the%20clock%20without%20the%20subscription%20(%2449.99%20yearly%20or%20%244.99%20monthly).%20But%20the%20unwind%20programs%2C%20which%20include%20meditations%2C%20music%2C%20and%20stories%2C%20aren't%20available%20unless%20you%20subscribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20portable%5C%22%3EBest%20portable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Casper%20Glow%20Light%20is%20a%20small%2C%20portable%20cylinder%20that%20you%20control%20with%20just%20a%20few%20gestures%3A%20flip%20to%20turn%20on%2C%20rotate%20to%20adjust%20the%20light%20intensity%2C%20and%20wiggle%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20night%20light.%20The%20device%20is%20softly%20lit%20and%20smartly%20designed%20with%20gentle%2C%20warm%20hues%20for%20a%20better%20sleep%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20light%20charges%20wirelessly%20and%20pairs%20with%20an%20intuitive%20app%20(available%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1398999798%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.casper.nova%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E).%20While%20you%20can%20operate%20the%20light%20without%20it%2C%20the%20app%20is%20a%20must%20to%20set%20wake-up%20and%20wind-down%20times%2C%20which%20cue%20a%20sunset%20or%20sunrise%20that%20can%20last%20from%2015%20to%2090%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20unique%20features%20of%20the%20Glow%20Light%20is%20that%20it%20synchronizes%20with%20other%20Glow%20Lights%20to%20make%20pretty%20light%20shows.%20Once%20you%20have%20more%20than%20one%2C%20you%20can%20name%20each%20and%20group%20or%20ungroup%20them%20through%20the%20app.%20I%20used%20two%20lights%20together%20and%20found%20they%20set%20a%20tranquil%20ambiance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20touches%20one%20of%20two%20glowing%20Casper%20Glow%20Lights%20on%20a%20wooden%20nightstand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fbc2c4250e71a0011556f29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECasper's%20Glow%20Light%20is%20portable%20and%20gesture-controlled%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20a%20unique%2C%20silent%20option%20for%20a%20wake-up%20alarm.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20alarm%20clock%20can%20also%20be%20used%20as%20a%20portable%20night%20light.%20This%20feature%20is%20useful%20when%20you%20want%20to%20find%20your%20way%20at%20night%20without%20bright%20lights.%20It%20was%20fun%20to%20carry%20around%20when%20I%20needed%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20in%20the%20dark.%20It's%20made%20with%20polycarbonate%20to%20resist%20bumps%20and%20endure%20falls%2C%20so%20it's%20also%20great%20for%20kids%20to%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFalling%20asleep%20with%20the%20Glow%20Lights%20was%20a%20treat.%20The%20soft%2C%20warm%20lights%20create%20a%20peaceful%20sleep%20environment%2C%20gradually%20dim%20to%20slowly%20relax%20you%2C%20and%20then%20turn%20completely%20off%20for%20total%20darkness.%20The%20Casper%20Glow%20Lights%20are%20made%20with%20high-quality%20warm%20LEDs%20that%20were%20effective%20in%20waking%20me%20up%20gently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20device%20focuses%20solely%20on%20effective%20light%20therapy%2C%20and%20unlike%20other%20models%20we%20tested%2C%20there%20are%20no%20sound%20options.%20It%20might%20not%20be%20ideal%20for%20heavy%20sleepers%20who%20need%20noise%20to%20wake%20up%3B%20you'll%20still%20need%20to%20set%20a%20separate%2C%20audible