larm%20and%20when%20you%20want%20to%20set%20the%20device%20to%20start%20gradually%20brightening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20get%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20functionality%20from%20the%20clock%20without%20the%20subscription%20(%2449.99%20a%20year%20or%20%244.99%20a%20month).%20But%20the%20unwind%20programs%2C%20which%20include%20meditations%2C%20music%2C%20and%20stories%2C%20aren't%20available%20unless%20you%20subscribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20portable%3A%20Casper%20Glow%20Light%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20touches%20one%20of%20two%20glowing%20Casper%20Glow%20Lights%20on%20a%20wooden%20nightstand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fbc2c4250e71a0011556f29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECasper's%20Glow%20Light%20is%20portable%20and%20gesture-controlled%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20a%20unique%2C%20silent%20option%20for%20a%20wake-up%20alarm.%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Hernandez%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20shut%20off%20the%20LED%20display%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20N%2FA%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmartphone%20compatibility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1398999798%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.casper.nova%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Android%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20changing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYellow%20only%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Beautiful%20warm%20lights%2C%20portable%2C%20pairs%20with%20multiple%20Glow%20Lights%20for%20a%20bedroom%20light%20show%2C%20intuitive%20and%20easy%20to%20operate%20with%20simple%20gestures%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong