C%20or%20both%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20alarms%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2016%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeekday%2Fweekend%20alarm%20setting%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESnooze%20duration%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%201%20to%2020%20minutes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20backup%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20No%2C%20but%20the%20device%20will%20work%20for%208%20hours%20during%20a%20power%20outage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20goal%20is%20a%20completely%20silent%20wake-up%2C%20the%20Philips%20SmartSleep%20Connected%20light%20might%20work%20for%20you.%20Before%20your%20alarm%20is%20scheduled%20to%20go%20off%2C%20it%20dimly%20lights%20up%20and%20then%20gradually%20brightens%20as%20your%20wake-up%20time%20approaches.%20There%20are%20sound%20options%2C%20too%2C%20if%20you%20need%20them%2C%20including%20FM%20radio.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou%20can%20increase%20the%20brightness%20level%20(or%20fully%20go%20without%20the%20light).%20It%20gets%20pretty%20intense%2C%20which%20you%20might%20need%20if%20you're%20a%20deep%20sleeper.%20I%20found%20that%20I%20wasn't%20disturbed%20by%20the%20light%20when%20it%20was%20on%20my%20partner's%20nightstand%20if%20I%20was%20facing%20the%20other%20direction.%20But%20if%20your%20partner%20is%20a%20light%20sleeper%2C%20they%20may%20wake%20up%20from%20the%20brightness.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20everything%20about%20the%20SmartSleep%20Connected%20is%20customizable.%20You%20can%20set%20over%20a%20dozen%20alarms%20with%20different%20light%20hues%2C%20several%20sound%20options%20%E2%80%94%20from%20waves%20to%20birds%20to%20Nepal%20bowls%20%E2%80%94%20and%20varying%20snooze%20lengths.%20You%20can%20choose%20how%20long%20before%20your%20alarm%20goes%20off%20you%20want%20the%20wake-up%20cycle%20to%20begin%2C%20between%205%20and%2040%20minutes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20need%20the%20accompanying%20SleepMapper%20app%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fsleepmapper%2Fid1258577276%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.philips.src.hss%26hl%3Den_US%26gl%3DUS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E)%20for%20most%20of%20this%20functionality.%20The%20app%20is%20easier%20than%20the%20on-device%20controls%2C%20which%20could%20be%20a%20bit%20clunky.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWake-up%20lights%20don't%20work%20for%20everyone.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20found%20it%20pretty%20ineffective%20when%20I%20used%20a%20sleep%20mask.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20wearable%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20is%20wearing%20a%20Fitbit%20Charge%205%20on%20their%20wrist.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F635c193b6c9ef40018131744%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fitbit%20Charge%205%20multifunctions%20as%20a%20sleep%20and%20health%20tracker%20that%20will%20make%20an%20impact%20morning%20to%20night%2C%20and%20it%20has%20a%20long%20weeklong%20battery%20life%20that%20pricier%2C%20smart%20watches%20still%20lack.%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlarm%20style%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Vibration%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20alarms%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%208%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeekday%2Fweekend%20alarm%20setting%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESnooze%20duration%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%209%20minutes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20backup%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20No%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20reliable%2C%20difficult-to-ignore%2C%20and%20nearly%20silent%20alarm%2C%20a%20wearable%20is%20the%20way%20to%20go.%20Usually%2C%20I%20wear%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20and%20am%20consistently%20awoken%20when%20it%20vibrates%20on%20my%20wrist%20when%20the%20alarm%20goes%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20Apple%20Watch%20battery%20only%20lasts%20around%2018%20hours%2C%20and%20not%20everyone%20remembers%20to%20charge%20their%20watch%20every%20night%20before%20bed.%20The%20Fitbit%20Charge%206%20can%20go%20about%20a%20week%20before%20you%20need%20to%20plug%20it%20in.%20Plus%2C%20many%20Fitbit%20models%20are%20at%20least%20%24100%20less%20than%20an%20Apple%20Watch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20set%20up%20to%20eight%20alarms%20right%20on%20the%20device%20and%20choose%20each%20day%20you%20want%20it%20to%20go%20off.%20The%20buzzing%20is%20very%20insistent%20and%20can%20be%20pretty%20jarring.%20It%20only%20vibrates%20for%20about%2015%20seconds%20before%20automatically%20snoozing%20for%209%20minutes%2C%20and%20there%20isn't%20a%20way%20to%20change%20either%20duration.%20It%20would%20be%20nice%20if%20there%20was%20a%20bit%20more%20personalization.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20Charge%20is%20also%20a%20sleep%20tracker%2C%20it%20monitors%20when%20you%20go%20to%20bed%20and%20get%20up.%20I%20didn't%20find%20this%20perfectly%20accurate%20(it%20said%20I%20was%20awake%20for%20much%20longer%20than%20I%20was%20one%20night)%2C%20but%20it%20still%20offered%20some%20useful%20insights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20optional%20%26quot%3Bsmart%20wake%26quot%3B%20feature%20on%20the%20alarm%20that%20will%20detect%20when%20you're%20in%20a%20lighter%20stage%20of%20your%20sleep%20cycle%20and%20will%20wake%20you%20up%20then%2C%20up%20to%2030%20minutes%20before%20your%20alarm%20is%20scheduled%20to%20go%20off.%20This%20is%20supposed%20to%20make%20you%20feel%20less%20groggy%20than%20if%20you%20woke%20from%20a%20deeper%20sleep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Charge%205%20is%20one%20of%20Insider%20Reviews'%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-fitbit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavorite%20Fitbits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20especially%20good%20for%20fitness%20and%20sleep%20tracking.%20If%20you%20don't%20need%20as%20many%20bells%20and%20whistles%2C%20the%20brand's%20other%20wearables%20have%20similar%20vibrating%20alarms.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-58697-20%26h%3Df24983411877a9d9c262243428d0dab753cdf5d1384972bdb93260dab41a8b4c%26postID%3D635c1675c4cc6f12bf064882%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-silent-alarm-clocks%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB08DFDP1TR%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFitbit%20Inspire%202%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20great%20budget%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEditor's%20note%20March%202024%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Fitbit%20has%20since%20released%20a%20new%20version%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-58697-20%26h%3D97348aa33088023c9c7cdb0ae7b8137a92117e793d3f1e8c626b5b64f58ee0e3%26postID%3D635c1675c4cc6f12bf064882%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-silent-alarm-clocks%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FFitbit-Exercise-Equipment-Membership-Porcelain%252Fdp%252FB0CC63GZ3R%253F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECharge%206%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20builds%20on%20the%20best%20features%20of%20its%20predecessor%2C%20and%20now%20includes%20Google%20Wallet%20and%20Map%20features%2C%20a%20built-in%20heart%20rate%20monitor%2C%20twice%20as%20many%20exercise%20modes%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20vibrating%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sonic%20Alert%20Sonic%20Bomb%20Dual%20Extra-Loud%20Alarm%20Clock%20with%20Bed%20Shaker%20sits%20on%20a%20nightstand%20and%20reads%203%3A25.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F635c19dc6c9ef40018131767%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sonic%20Bomb%20Extra-Loud%20Alarm%20Clock%20has%20an%20intense%20puck-like%20shaker%20attachment%20that%20you%20place%20under%20your%20mattress%2C%20and%20will%20certainly%20jolt%20you%20awake.%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlarm%20style%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EVibration%2C%20sound%2C%20or%20both%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20alarms%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETwo%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeekday%2Fweekend%20alarm%20setting%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESnooze%20duration%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%201%20to%2030%20minutes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20backup%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20name%2C%20the%20Sonic%20Bomb%20Extra-Loud%20Alarm%20Clock%20doesn't%20solely%20rely%20on%20sound%20to%20wake%20you%20up.%20Put%20the%20puck-like%20shaker%20under%20your%20mattress%2C%20and%20the%20vibration%20will%20almost%20certainly%20jolt%20you%20awake.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20exactly%20a%20pleasant%20way%20to%20wake%20up%2C%20and%20the%20vibration%20isn't%20silent%20either.%20But%20for%20people%20who%20are%20deaf%20or%20hard%20of%20hearing%2C%20a%20physical%20alarm%20that%20isn't%20sound-based%20could%20be%20useful%20if%20a%20light-based%20alarm%20isn't%20reliable%20enough.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20sleep%20with%20a%20partner%20in%20your%20bed%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20this%20alarm%20will%20wake%20them%20up%20too.%20Even%20with%20a%20very%20thick%20mattress%2C%20I%20could%20feel%20the%20alarm%20buzzing%20from%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20bed.%20The%20resulting%20sound%20wasn't%20very%20muffled%2C%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20that%20this%20alarm%20was%20pretty%20customizable%20for%20the%20price.%20You%20can%20wake%20up%20with%20just%20the%20vibration%20or%20a%20buzzing%20sound%20or%20combine%20them.%20The%20tone%20of%20the%20buzzer%20can%20be%20changed%2C%20and%20you%20can%20opt%20to%20turn%20the%20flashing%20lights%20on%20or%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20impressed%20by%20the%20customizable%20snooze%20functionality.%20The%20ability%20to%20change%20the%20duration%20isn't%20something%20you%20always%20find%20on%20budget-friendly%20alarm%20clocks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20two%20alarms%2C%20you%20have%20to%20remember%20to%20toggle%20between%20them%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20your%20weekday%20alarm%20going%20off%20on%20Saturdays%2C%20though%20you%20can%20choose%20to%20have%20both%20go%20off%20every%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20headphones%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20lies%20in%20bed%20wearing%20AcousticSheep%20SleepPhones%20wireless%20headphones.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F635c1e793e1cce00181b85b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20fall%20asleep%20asleep%20to%20music%20or%20podcasts%20and%20wake%20up%20with%20sound%20cues%20with%20the%20SleepPhones%2C%20but%20you%20will%20need%20to%20download%20a%20third-party%20alarm%20app.%3Cp%3EAcousticSheep%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlarm%20style%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESound%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20alarms%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EN%2FA%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeekday%2Fweekend%20alarm%20setting%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EN%2FA%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESnooze%20duration%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20N%2FA%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20backup%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20like%20to%20fall%20asleep%20to%20music%20or%20podcasts%20and%20wake%20up%20with%20sound%20cues%2C%20a%20comfortable%20pair%20of%20sleep%20headphones%20can%20be%20a%20great%20solution.%20AcousticSheep's%20SleepPhones%20are%20breathable%20and%20washable%20and%20can%20go%20days%20without%20you%20needing%20to%20charge%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20listen%20to%20audiobooks%20to%20fall%20asleep%2C%20and%20it%20was%20nice%20knowing%20that%20my%20alarm%20would%20play%20through%20the%20headphones%20in%20the%20morning.%20After%20the%20alarm%20went%20off%2C%20I%20would%20invariably%20leave%20the%20headphones%20on%20and%20paired%20to%20my%20phone%20by%20accident.%20Yet%20they%20lasted%20well%20over%20a%20week%20without%20me%20needing%20to%20charge%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20did%20need%20to%20charge%20the%20headphones%2C%20I%20pulled%20the%20module%20out%20of%20a%20pouch%20in%20the%20headband.%20You%20can%20wash%20the%20SleepPhones%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20remove%20all%20the%20components%20first.%20Unlike%20some%20sleep%20headphones%20I%20tried%2C%20the%20pouch%20concealed%20any%20blinking%20light%20you%20sometimes%20get%20with%20Bluetooth%20devices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20did%20need%20to%20download%20a%20third-party%20alarm%20app.%20This%20was%20true%20of%20every%20pair%20of%20headphones%20I%20tried.%20Even%20if%20they%20were%20connected%20to%20my%20iPhone%2C%20the%20native%20alarm%20app%20would%20play%20through%20the%20phone's%20speakers%20instead%20of%20to%20my%20headphones.%20That%20really%20defeats%20the%20purpose%20if%20you're%20trying%20not%20to%20wake%20anyone%20else%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SleepPhones%20are%20available%20in%20either%20fleece%20or%20a%20more%20breathable%20fabric%20that%20reminded%20me%20of%20workout%20shorts.%20While%20the%20bands%20come%20in%20three%20sizes%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20couldn't%20adjust%20the%20size%20was%20a%20problem.%20The%20medium%20sometimes%20felt%20too%20constricting%20when%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20sleep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20silent%20alarm%20clocks%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20vibration%20puck%20of%20the%20Sonic%20Alert%20Sonic%20Boom%20alarm%20rests%20between%20two%20mattresses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F635c20403e1cce00181b8678%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20tested%20seven%20different%20silent%20alarm%20clocks%20according%20to%20setup%2C%20performance%2C%20durability%2C%20special%20features%2C%20and%20long-term%20use.%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20getting%20insight%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffindadoctor.spectrumhealth.org%2Fphysician%2Fprofile%2F3217%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKelly%20Waters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20MD%2C%20a%20sleep%20specialist%20at%20Spectrum%20Health%2C%20I%20tested%20seven%20different%20silent%20alarm%20clocks%20and%20evaluated%20them%20based%20on%20the%20following%20criteria%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetup%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20each%20alarm%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20set%20it%20up%20without%20reading%20the%20instructions%20to%20see%20how%20intuitive%20they%20were.%20I%20then%20set%20them%20up%20again%20after%20reading%20the%20manual%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20directions%20were%20easy%20to%20follow.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20used%20each%20alarm%20for%20at%20least%20three%20nights.%20I%20evaluated%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20set%20alarms%2C%20whether%20the%20alarm%20consistently%20woke%20me%20up%2C%20and%20how%20difficult%20it%20was%20to%20shut%20off%20and%20snooze%20the%20alarms.%20For%20at%20least%20one%20night%2C%20I%20put%20the%20alarm%20on%20my%20partner's%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20or%20had%20him%20use%20it%20so%20I%20could%20see%20if%20I%20was%20disturbed%20when%20he%20woke%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20features%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20tested%20features%20such%20as%20Bluetooth%20or%20WiFi%20connectivity%2C%20accompanying%20mobile%20apps%2C%20wind-down%20programs%2C%20and%20night%20lights%20to%20see%20if%20they%20were%20helpful%20and%20simple%20to%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20test%20how%20breakable%20each%20alarm%20clock%20was%2C%20I%20pushed%20each%20off%20my%20nightstand.%20They%20all%20passed%20this%20test%2C%20though%20the%20Mesqool's%20battery%20cover%20did%20pop%20off.%20(I%20was%20able%20to%20put%20it%20back%20on.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-term%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20testing%2C%20I'm%20continuing%20to%20use%20our%20top%20picks%20to%20monitor%20for%20durability%20and%20usability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESilent%20alarm%20clock%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Philips%20SmartSleep%20Connected%20wake-up%20light%20glows%20yellow%20on%20a%20nightstand%20near%20a%20pair%20of%20glasses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F635c1fa93e1cce00181b8619%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20McGrath%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20a%20silent%20alarm%20clock%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20ways%20to%20look%20at%20it%3A%20It's%20either%20something%20like%20a%20wake-up%20light%20that%20makes%20no%20noise%2C%20or%20it's%20something%20like%20a%20vibrating%20alarm%20that%2C%20while%20not%20necessarily%20silent%2C%20can%20wake%20up%20someone%20who%20can't%20hear%20a%20sound-based%20alarm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20silent%20alarm%20clocks%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20in%20sleep%2C%20the%20brain%20is%20still%20processing%20your%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffindadoctor.spectrumhealth.org%2Fphysician%2Fprofile%2F3217%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKelly%20Waters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20MD%2C%20a%20sleep%20specialist%20at%20Spectrum%20Health%2C%20told%20Insider%20Reviews%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BAny%20abrupt%20change%20to%20that%20stasis%20will%20elicit%20a%20response%2C%20whether%20the%20abrupt%20noise%20of%20an%20alarm%2C%20vibration%2C%20movement%2C%20or%20light.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20she%20said%20not%20everyone%20responds%20to%20the%20same%20type%20of%20wake-up%20cue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20sunrise%20or%20wake-up%20light%20alarm%20clocks%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20rely%20on%20the%20natural%20waking%20response%20to%20ambient%20light%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Waters.%20%26quot%3BThe%20brain%20will%20be%20susceptible%20to%20waking%20when%20it%20is%20naturally%20in%20lighter%20sleep.%26quot%3B%20She%20warns%20that%20these%20aren't%20precise%20and%20may%20not%20work%20for%20everyone%2C%20including%20heavy%20sleepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-silent-alarm-clocks%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709931248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F635c17586c9ef4001813169f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-silent-alarm-clocks%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20tested%20several%20options%20to%20find%20the%20best%20silent%20alarm%20clocks%20for%20people%20who%20are%20hard%20of%20hearing%20or%20those%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20wake%20up%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jmcgrath%40insider.com%20(Jenny%20McGrath)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-silent-alarm-clocks%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shawn%20Mendes%20Plots%20Rock%20in%20Rio%20Performance%2C%20His%20First%20Since%20Canceling%20Tour%20to%20Prioritize%20Mental%20Health%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709930903000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https