%2Fpakistan%2Fimf-gives-cold-shoulder-to-imran-khan-as-it-refuses-to-involve-into-domestic-politics%2Famp_articleshow%2F108335401.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20Among%2039%20Names%20In%20Congress'%201st%20Lok%20Sabha%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20week%20after%20the%20BJP%20announced%20its%20first%20list%20of%20195%20candidates%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20come%20up%20with%20its%20answer%20in%20the%20form%20of%2039%20names%2C%20including%20those%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-finalises-seats-in-these-states-announcement-soon-5197784%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20and%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20will%20contest%20from%20Wayanad%20in%20Kerala%20but%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20he%20will%20also%20be%20fielded%20from%20Amethi%2C%20like%20in%202019.%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20will%20fight%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20a%20seat%20he%20has%20held%20for%20three%20terms%2C%20while%20Mr%20Baghel%20will%20contest%20from%20Rajnandgaon%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20other%20big%20names%20on%20the%20list%20are%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20who%20will%20contest%20from%20Alappuzha%20in%20Kerala%20-%20a%20seat%20he%20had%20won%20in%202014%20-%20and%20DK%20Suresh%2C%20brother%20of%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Bengaluru%20Rural.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20have%20been%20announced%20primarily%20for%20some%20southern%20and%20northeastern%20states%20and%20the%20only%20outliers%20are%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Lakshadweep.%C2%A0At%2016%2C%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20candidates%20have%20been%20announced%20from%20Kerala%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20expected%20to%20leave%20the%20remaining%20four%20seats%20for%20its%20allies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20names%20have%20been%20announced%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20six%20from%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20four%20from%20Telangana.%20The%20remaining%20are%20from%20Meghalaya%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Tripura%20and%20Lakshadweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20on%20the%20south%20is%20deliberate%20because%20not%20only%20does%20the%20Congress%20have%20its%20governments%20in%20the%20states%20of%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20the%20only%20region%20in%20the%20country%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20relatively%20weak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20On%20Communities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20announcing%20the%20names%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Venugopal%20said%20the%20candidates%20had%20been%20picked%20by%20the%20Congress%20Central%20Election%20Committee.%20He%20emphasised%20that%2024%20of%20the%2039%20candidates%20are%20from%20the%20OBC%2C%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20minority%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20this%20list%20is%20a%20start%20and%20more%20names%20can%20be%20expected%20as%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20finalises%20seat-sharing%20in%20some%20of%20the%20remaining%20states%2C%20including%20Maharashtra.%20Deciding%20on%20pacts%20for%20the%20state%2C%20which%20sends%20the%20second-highest%20number%20of%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20troublesome%20for%20both%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20behind%20the%20delay%20could%20also%20be%20the%20fact%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20busy%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20which%20is%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20will%20end%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20March%2017.%20Mr%20Venugopal%20said%20there%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20rally%20in%20the%20city%20on%20that%20day%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20all%20INDIA%20party%20leaders%20are%20being%20invited%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709919000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fq8adv0i8_rahul-gandhi_625x300