an-in-new-ad-the-collab-you-didnt-know-you-needed%2Farticleshow%2F108335098.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Can't%20Even%20Flush%26quot%3B%3A%20Water%20Crisis%20Takes%20Toll%20On%20Bengaluru%20Residents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20severe%20water%20crisis%20gripping%20Bengaluru%2C%20residents%2C%20schools%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20apartment%20complexes%20are%20facing%20acute%20shortages.%20The%20situation%20has%20reached%20critical%20levels%2C%20as%20highlighted%20by%20a%20Reddit%20post%20shedding%20light%20on%20the%20challenges%20encountered%20by%20residents%20of%20a%20housing%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20more%20than%20a%20month%20since%20we%20received%20regular%20round-the-clock%20supply%20of%20water%20in%20our%20flat%20in%20Prestige%20Falcon%20City.%20Now%20the%20situation%20is%20beyond%20the%20limits%20of%20what%20can%20be%20called%20inhabitable.%20No%20water%20during%20the%20daytime%2C%20when%20we%20do%20get%20it%20during%20the%20night%2C%20it's%20just%20muddy%20water%20unfit%20for%20bathing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20get%20to%20smell%20the%20stink%20of%20unflushed%20human%20excreta%20in%20toilet%20bowls%20from%20far%20away.%20It's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20see%20a%20line%20of%20residents%20going%20to%20the%20nearby%20Forum%20Mall%20to%20do%20their%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residents'%20association%20recommended%20using%20wet%20wipes%20and%20disposable%20utensils%20in%20light%20of%20the%20crisis%2C%20citing%20the%20challenges%20of%20traditional%20washing%20methods.%20Financial%20pressure%20mounts%20as%20residents%2C%20who%20are%20already%20dealing%20with%20housing%20loans%2C%20struggle%20with%20unacceptable%20living%20conditions.%20The%20message%20cautioned%20prospective%20buyers%20against%20purchasing%20apartments%20that%20solely%20rely%20on%20tanker%20water%20and%20encouraged%