20partner%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20announced%20senior%20party%20leader%20Annie%20Raja%20as%20its%20candidate%20for%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-congress-annie-raja-cpi-wayanad-rahul-gandhi%5C%22%3E%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Raja%20had%20said%20that%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20that%20has%20to%20decide%20whether%20it%20wants%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Left%20forces%20and%20she%20hopes%20that%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20sense%20will%20prevail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenugopal%20however%2C%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20focus%20is%20to%20reduce%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20in%20the%20maximum%20possible%20way%20to%20go%20with%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20but%20there%20are%20issues%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Assam%20and%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20sort%20it%20out.%20Congress%20party%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20to%20reduce%20BJP%20seats%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20sacrifice%20anything.%20But%20others%20also%20need%20to%20do%20that.%20In%20some%20states%20others%20also%20need%20to%20move%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20still%20speculation%20about%20whether%20Gandhi%20will%20also%20contest%20from%20his%20old%20turf%20of%20Amethi%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20fielded%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20repeat%20her%202019%20performance%2C%20the%20Congress%20list%20is%20silent%20on%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKerala%20surprise%20and%20other%20sitting%20MPs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20includes%20a%20total%20of%2017%20sitting%20MPs%20including%20Thiruvananthapuram%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20who%20will%20seek%20re-election%20for%20a%20fourth%20term%20from%20the%20constituency%20and%20take%20on%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20has%20also%20been%20given%20a%20ticket%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Rajnandgaon%20constituency.%20He%20will%20take%20on%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20sitting%20MP%20Santosh%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20however%20dropped%20a%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Thrissur%20constituency%20T.N.%20Prathapan%20and%20instead%20fielded%20K.%20Muraleedharan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20field%20Muraleedharan%20who%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Vadakara%2C%20from%20Thrissur%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20his%20sister%20Padmaja%20Venugopal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-congress-there-is-no-leadership-padmaja-venugopal-joins-bjp-5195697%5C%22%3Ejoining%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20saffron%20party%20in%20its%20list%20announced%20last%20week%2C%20has%20however%20fielded%20Suresh%20Gopi%20from%20Thrissur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenugopal%20who%20is%20a%20sitting%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20will%20also%20contest%20the%20elections%20from%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Alappuzha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20MPs%20that%20have%20been%20fielded%20include%20Jyotsna%20Mahant%20from%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Korba%2C%C2%A0%20Kerala%20MPs%20V.K%20Sreekandan%20(Palakkad)%2C%20M.K%20Raghavan%20(Kozhikode)%2C%20K.%20Sudhakaran%20(Kannur)%2C%20Rajmohan%20Unnithan%20(Kasargod)%2C%20Ramya%20Haridas%20(Alathur)%2C%20Beny%20Behanan%20(Chalakundy)%2C%20Hibi%20Eden%20(Ernakulam)%2C%20Dean%20Kuriakose%20(Idukki)%2C%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20(Thiruvananthapuram)%2C%20K%20Suresh%20(Mavelikkara)%2C%20Anto%20Antony%20(Pathanamthitta)%2C%20Adoor%20Prakash%20(Attingal)%2C%20and%20Vincent%20H%20Pala%20from%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20Shillong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20headway%20with%20TMC%2C%20Meghalaya%20candidates%20named%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20indication%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20Trin