26quot%3BAt%20the%20start%2C%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20tentative%20(while%20batting)%20to%20get%20going%2C%20but%20once%20I%20got%20my%20eye%20in%20it%20got%20much%20easier.%20There%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20reverse%20and%20those%20are%20two%20(Anderson%20and%20Stokes)%20top-quality%20bowlers%20you%20are%20facing.%20It%20was%20challenging%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20used%20to%20the%20wicket.%20It%20was%20challenging%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20because%20of%20my%20health%20issues%20(had%20problems%20with%20his%20gut%20health)%20which%20are%20well-documented%2C%20so%20when%20you%20are%20sitting%20at%20home%20and%20not%20doing%20anything%2C%20it%20surely%20wasn't%20a%20pleasant%20feeling%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20opportunity%20whenever%20it%20comes.%20It's%20always%20great%20to%20have%20familiar%20faces%20(while%20on%20debut)%2C%20especially%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20debutant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20receiving%20his%20Test%20cap%20from%20a%20teammate%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20veteran%20of%20many%20battles%20and%20is%20playing%20his%20100th%20Test%20at%20Dharamshala%2C%20Padikkal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20special%20feeling%20(getting%20his%20debut%20Test%20cap)%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20circumstances%2C%20to%20live%20in%20that%20dream%20is%20something%20special.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20ruling%20the%20roost%20in%20the%20first%20two%20sessions%20of%20play%20on%20Day%202%2C%20the%20hosts%20ceded%20ground%20in%20the%20session%20after%20Tea%20as%20it%20suffered%20a%20late-order%20collapse%20to%20be%20reduced%20to%20428%2F8.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20skipper%20Rohit%20and%20Shubhman%20bossed%20the%20visitors%20in%20the%20opening%20session%20and%20after%20Lunch%2C%20both%20bringing%20up%20fine%20centuries%20in%20the%20process%2C%20England%20made%20a%20comeback%20of%20sorts%20largely%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20four-wicket%20haul%20by%20Somerset%20off-spinner%20Shoaib%20Bashir%2C%20who%20found%20appre