nand%20College%20in%202021%20after%20being%20implicated%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20still%20feels%20as%20if%20he%20is%20in%20a%20jail%20cell%20after%20spending%20seven%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20released%20from%20the%20Nagpur%20Central%20Jail%20on%20Thursday%2C%20two%20days%20after%20his%20acquittal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20family%2C%20he%20said%20they%20survived%20only%20on%20hope%20but%20regretted%20not%20being%20able%20to%20meet%20his%20mother%20on%20her%20deathbed%20and%20claimed%20he%20was%20denied%20bail%20to%20perform%20her%20last%20rites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20going%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20press%20because%20you%20supported%20me.%20My%20family%20faced%20stigma%20and%20I%20was%20called%20a%20terrorist%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20with%20tears%20in%20his%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20his%20%26quot%3Bjail%20ordeal%26quot%3B%20Saibaba%20claimed%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20live%20in%20cramped%20conditions%20and%20was%20denied%20medicines%20and%20treatment%20prescribed%20by%20doctors%20for%20his%20ailing%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20imprisoned%20in%20a%20jail%20which%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%201%2C500%20inmates%20but%203%2C000%20people%20were%20lodged%20there%20in%20cramped%20conditions.%20There%20was%20no%20space%20to%20even%20sleep.%20Without%20a%20wheelchair%20I%20use%20to%20struggle%20to%20use%20toilet%2C%20take%20bath%20or%20even%20fetch%20myself%20a%20class%20of%20water.%20There%20was%20not%20even%20a%20single%20ramp%20in%20the%20prison%20for%20people%20like%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20chocked%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20I%20am%20alive%20in%20front%20of%20you.%20But%20every%20organ%20of%20my%20body%20is%20failing.%20I%20faced%20many%20medical%20emergencies%20in%20the%20jail%20but%20they%20only%20gave%20me%20painkillers%20and%20did%20a%20few%20tests%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20said%20that%20his%20family%20faced%20stigma%20because%20he%20was%20framed%20in%20a%20case%20under%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20was%20lodged%20in%20the%20Nagpur%20Central%20Jail%20since%202017%20after%20his%20conviction%20by%20a%20trial%20court%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Gadchiroli%20district.%20Before%20that%2C%20he%20was%20in%20prison%20from%202014%20to%202016%20and%20was%20subsequently%20granted%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20still%20not%20able%20to%20register%20that%20I%20am%20free.%20I%20feel%20I%20am%20still%20lodged%20in%20the%20notorious%20jail%20cell.%20It%20was%20like%20an%20'agni%20pariksha'%20for%20me.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20through%20a%20test%20by%20fire%20twice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanking%20his%20lawyers%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20activists%2C%20he%20said%20one%20his%20lawyers%20fought%20his%20case%20without%20any%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20lawyer%20got%20jailed%20because%20of%20supporting%20me.%20During%20the%20trial%2C%20certain%20police%20officers%20threatened%20my%20lawyers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709913780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F0m570a5o_gn-saibaba-ani_625x300_08_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcant-live-without-teaching-want-my-job-back-ex-professor-gn-saibaba-5202102%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20G%20N%20Saibaba%20demanded%20that%20he%20be%20reinstated%20by%20the%20varsity%20and%20compensated%20for%20the%20lost%20years%20of%20service%20following%20his%20acquittal%20by%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20in%20a%20Maoist%20links%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2