elivery-personnel-5201726%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Finternational-womens-day-zomato-unveils-new-dress-code-for-female-delivery-personnel-5201726%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Finternational-womens-day-zomato-unveils-new-dress-code-for-female-delivery-personnel-5201726%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Fields%20Chhattisgarh's%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20From%20BJP%20Stronghold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20is%20back%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20race%20after%20nearly%20a%20decade.%20His%20name%20was%20announced%20today%20in%20the%20Congress%20party's%20first%20candidate%20list%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20electtions.%20Mr%20Baghel%20will%20contest%20the%20polls%20from%20Rajnandgaon%2C%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20BJP%20stronghold.%20Mr%20Baghel%20lost%20the%20Parliamentary%20elections%20in%202009%20from%20Raipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20Santosh%20Pandey%2C%20who%20has%20been%20refielded%20from%20Rajnandgaon%2C%20has%20represented%20the%20constituency%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2062-year-old%20served%20as%20the%20third%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20from%202018%20to%202023.%20He%20was%20the%20president%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20Pradesh%20Congress%20from%202014%20to%202019%2C%20and%20currently%20represents%20the%20Patan%20constituency%20in%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Legislative%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Mr%20Baghel's%20name%2C%20five%20other%20candidates%20from%20Chhattisgarh%20have%20been%20announced%3A%20Shivkumar%20Dahariya%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Jangir-Champa%2C%20Jyotsana%20Mahant%20will%20contest%20from%20Korba%2C%20Rajendra%20Sahu%20from%20Durg%2C%20Vikas%20Upadhay%20from%20Raipur%2C%20Tamradhwaj%20Sahu%20from%20Mahasamund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20first%20list%20with%2039%20names%20features%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20but%20appears%20fairly%20limited%20compared%20to%20BJP's%20195%20which%20included%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%2034%20Central%20and%20state%20ministers.%20The%20party%20has%20announced%20names%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Lakshadweep%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Tripura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20didn't%20mention%20states%20that%20have%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20-%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(80)%2C%20Maharashtra%20(48)%2C%20West%20Bengal%20(42)%20and%20Bihar%20(40)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20whose%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%202.0%20is%20currently%20passing%20through%20Gujarat%2C%20will%20seek%20re-election%20from%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20seat.%20He%20may%20also%20contest%20from%20Amethi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20from%20Raebareli%2C%20a%20seat%20that%20was%20previously%20held%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%20Both%20the%20seats%20are%20considered%20bastions%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20and%20the%20local%20units%20of%20the%20Congress%20have%20demanded%20that%20the%20two%20scions%20of%20the%20Congress%20first%20family%20should%20contest%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%2039%20candidates%20announced%2C%2015%20are%20from%20Kerala%2C%20seven%20from%20Karnataka%20and%20six%20from%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20four%20from%20Telangana.%20Two%20from%20Meghalaya%20and%20one%20each%20from%20Nagaland%2C%20Tripura%2C%20Sikkim%20and%20Lakshwadeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20party's%20second%20Election%20Committee%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%20on%20March%2011%20in%20Delhi%20to%20discuss%20the%20candidates%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20The%20polls%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20held%20in%20April-May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709911380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fqpvi0ebo_cg-news-bhupesh-baghel-_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originI