-%20where%2010%20people%20were%20injured%20last%20week%20after%20a%20low-intensity%20explosive%2C%20or%20IED%2C%20was%20detonated%20during%20the%20lunch%20rush%20hour%20-%20will%20re-open%2C%20%26quot%3Bbrighter%20and%20stronger%26quot%3B%2C%20for%20business%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20the%20restaurant's%20HR%20head%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESridhar%20Murthy%20said%20work%20on%20repairing%20and%20rebuilding%20damaged%20parts%20of%20the%20cafe%20began%20immediately%20after%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20case%2C%20handed%20over%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20day%20NIA%20handed%20cafe%20to%20us%2C%20we%20began%20our%20work.%20We%20already%20had%20several%20meetings%20with%20our%20Managing%20Director%20and%20maintenance%20team.%20Within%2048%20hours%20all%20repair%20work%20was%20carried%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Murthy%20said%20the%20cafe%20-%20an%20iconic%20eatery%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Brookfield%20area%20-%20would%20re-open%20%26quot%3Bbrighter%20and%20stronger%26quot%3B%20than%20before.%20%26quot%3BOur%20team%20worked%20around%20the%20clock%2C%20even%20till%20this%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BFortunately%20there%20was%20no%20serious%20damage...%20and%20everyone%20suffered%20only%20minor%20injuries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cafe's%20co-owner%2C%20Divya%20Raghavendra%20Rao%2C%20said%20the%20opening%20'ceremony'%20would%20include%20a%20rendition%20of%20the%20national%20anthem.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20mantra.%20We%20have%20taken%20all%20precautions%20before%20re-opening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20administration%2C%20metal%20detectors%20have%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20entrance%20to%20screen%20customers%2C%20and%20staff%20have%20also%20been%20given%20handheld%20detectors.%20Additional%20CCTVs%20have%20been%20set%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20also%20said%20the%20cafe%20is%20cooperating%20with%20the%20authorities%20and%20had%20surrendered%20all%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20other%20information.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thankful%20to%20the%20government%20for%20helping%20us%20reopen%20so%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20wanted%20to%20teach%20us%20a%20lesson...%20but%20we%20will%20teach%20them%20a%20lesson.%20With%20blessings%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20we%20have%20reopened%20our%20cafe%20on%20occasion%20of%20Mahashivratri%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20defiantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENIA%20Takes%20Over%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%2C%20which%20took%20over%20this%20case%20on%20Monday%2C%20has%20announced%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20information%20about%20the%20suspected%20bomber%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20on%20the%20cafe's%20CCTV%20footage%20minutes%20before%20the%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20can%20be%20given%20to%20the%20central%20anti-terror%20agency%20via%20e-mail%20-%20info.blr.nia%40gov.in%20-%20or%20via%20one%20of%20two%20phone%20numbers%20-%20080-29510900%20and%208904241100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengaluru-rameshwaram-cafe-blast-nia-offers-rs-10-lakh-bounty-for-info-about-bomber-5190306%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru%20Cafe%20Blast%3A%20NIA's%2010%20Lakh%20Bounty%20For%20Info%20About%20Bomber%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProvisions%20of%20the%20stringent%20anti-terror%20law%20-%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20-%20and%20the%20Explosive%20Substances%20Act%20-%20have%20been%20invoked%20against%20those%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Blast%20Happened%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20he%20is%20seen%20wearing%20a%20cap%2C%20face%20mask%2C%20and%20sunglasses%2C%20and%20is%20dressed%20in%20dark%20trousers%20and%20a%20grey%20shirt.%20He%20is%20first