ents%20the%20Cultural%20Ambassador%20of%20The%20Year%20award%20to%20Maithili%20Thakur%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FuD0g9vkaxq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FuD0g9vkaxq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1765974175385079817%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20singer%20also%20shared%20a%20video%20with%20PM%20Modi%20after%20receiving%20the%20award.%20%26quot%3BI%20met%20you%20today.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%20in%20the%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-big-praise-for-bihar-based-singer-maithili-thakur-4897337%5C%22%3Epraised%20the%20young%20singer%3C%2Fa%3E's%20musical%20talent%20and%20also%20shared%20a%20popular%20Ram%20bhajan%20sung%20by%20her%20ahead%20of%20the%20mega%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20Ms%20Thakur's%20%26quot%3Bmelodious%20tunes%26quot%3B%20remind%20people%20of%20the%20life%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%20%26quot%3BThe%20occasion%20of%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20reminding%20my%20family%20members%20across%20the%20country%20of%20every%20incident%20related%20to%20the%20life%20and%20ideals%20of%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram.%20One%20such%20emotional%20incident%20is%20related%20to%20Shabari.%20Listen%2C%20to%20how%20Maithili%20Thakur%20ji%20has%20put%20it%20in%20her%20melodious%20tunes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Creators%20Awards%2C%20organised%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20celebrated%20digital%20creators%20across%2020%20categories%20that%20recognised%20their%20efforts%20in%20impacting%20social%20change%2C%20environmental%20sustainability%2C%20education%20and%20gaming%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%201.5%20lakh%20nominations%20were%20received%20and%2010%20lakh%20votes%20were%20cast%20for%20digital%20creators%20across%20categories.%20On%20Friday%2C%2023%20winners%2C%20including%20popular%20creators%20like%20Kabita%20Singh%20(Kabita's%20Kitchen)%2C%20Ankit%20Baiyanpuria%2C%20Kamiya%20Jani%20and%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20(BeerBiceps)%20were%20awarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709904600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fqbma5td_pm-modi-maithili-thakur_625x300_08_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftired-of-listening-to-me-pm-modis-banter-with-youtuber-maithili-thakur-goes-viral-5201212%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20shared%20a%20light-hearted%20moment%20with%20Bihar-based%20singer%20Maithili%20Thakur%20at%20the%20first-ever%20National%20Creators%20Award%20on%20Friday.%20The%20PM%20presented%20the%20'Cultural%20Ambassador%20of%20The%20Year'%20award%20to%20the%2023-year-old%20singer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftired-of-listening-to-me-pm-modis-banter-with-youtuber-maithili-thakur-goes-viral-5201212%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftired-of-listening-to-me-pm-modis-banter-with-youtuber-maithili-thakur-goes-viral-5201212%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftired-of-listening-to-me-pm-modis-banter-with-youtuber-maithili-thakur-goes-viral-5201212%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Challenges%20for%20the%20Army%3A%20Politicisation%2C%20Prioritising%20Counter-Insurgency%20and%20a%20Modernising%20Adversary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06155517%2FEffect-14-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20most%20ambitious%20and%20totally%20outdated%20military%20reform%20%E2%80%98Integrated%20Theatre%20Commands%20(ITCs)%E2%80%99%20appears%20to%20be%20dead%20and%20one%20wonders%20if%20it%20was%20ever%20a%20serious%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EITCs%20meant%20that%20elements%20of%20the%20three%20military%20services%20(two%2C%20the%20army%20and%20the%20air%20force%2C%20in%20case%20of%20land%20wars%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20with%20China%20and%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20with%20Pakistan)%20would%20be%20brought%20permanently%20under%20a%20single%20commander%20for%20jointness%20and%20synergy%20in%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJointness%20in%20operations%20implies%20that%20all%20services%20fight%20together%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98joint%20force%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20synergy%20means%20that%20they%20should%20be%20able%20to%20complement%20one%20another.%20For%20instance%2C%20army%20assets%20in%20the%20land%20domain%20should%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20hit%20the%20enemy%E2%80%99s%20assets%20in%20the%20air%20domain%2C%20such%20as%20fighters%20or%20incoming%20missiles.%20Thus%2C%20for%20land%20war%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98joint%20force%E2%80%99%20would%20comprise%20army%20and%20air%20force%20assets%20with%20cross-domain%20capability%20and%20with%20the%20army%20as%20the%20lead%20service%20since%20boots%20on%20the%20ground%20are%20essential%20for%20occupation%20of%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20veneer%20of%20ITCs%20which%20involved%20major%20structural%20reforms%2C%20the%20real%20purpose%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20to%20kill%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone%3A%20retain%20superannuating%20army%20chief%2C%20General%20Bipin%20Rawat%20in%20uniform%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20military%20served%20the%20ruling%20political%20party%E2%80%99s%20agenda%20rather%20than%20the%20national%20interest%20that%20it%20was%20constitutionally%20sworn%20to%20do.%20And%20to%20project%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20national%20security%20by%20ostensibly%20undertaking%20long%20pending%20military%20reforms%20to%20strengthen%20war%20preparedness.%20Never%20mind%20that%20those%20reforms%20were%20past%20their%20expiry%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20overdue%20reforms%20were%3A%20the%20post%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-chief-of-defence-staff-position-5908744%2F%5C%22%3EChief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20(CDS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20suggested%20by%20the%202002%20Group%20of%20Ministers%20recommendations%20following%20the%20Kargil%20review%20committee%20report%2C%20and%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20December%202016%20Shekatkar%20committee%20report%20to%20create%20ITCs%20to%20fight%20better%20on%20the%20military%20lines%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20China.%20These%20committees%20were%20constituted%20by%20the%20Vajpayee%20and%20Modi-led%20BJP%20governments%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeneral%20Rawat%20was%20ideal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bit%20on%20why%20General%20Rawat%20was%20ideal%20for%20the%20post%20of%20the%20CDS%20as%20envisioned%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20This%20was%20mostly%20as%20he%20was%20past%20master%20at%20projecting%20military%20victory%20where%20there%20was%20none.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20three-year%20tenure%20as%20army%20chief%2C%20Rawat%20planned%20the%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fsurgical-strikes-know-dont-know%5C%22%3E2016%20surgical%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ffour-reasons-india-has-little-reason-to-cheer-the-balakot-airstrike-and-its-aftermath%5C%22%3E2019%20Balakot%20air%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Pakistan.%20He%20also%20flexed%20military%20muscle%20against%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-india-bhutan-doklam-standoff-border-dispute%5C%22%3E2017%20Doklam%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20resulted%20in%20projecting%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%94%20by%20unscrupulous%20mainline%20media%20%E2%80%94%20as%20the%20sole%20leader%20with%20the%20courage%20to%20challenge%20both%20adversaries%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08170730%2FBipin_Rawat_Chief_of_Defence_Staff_CDS.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08170730%2FBipin_Rawat_Chief_of_Defence_Staff_CDS.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08170730%2FBipin_Rawat_Chief_of_Defence_Staff_CDS-250x300.jpg%20250w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBipin%20Rawat%2C%20Former%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20of%20the%20Indian%20Armed%20Forces.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FIntegrated%20Defence%20Staff%2FGODL%20License.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20was%20all%20three%20episodes%20were%20disastrous%20for%20India%20as%20they%20exposed%20the%20operational%20shortcomings%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF).%20This%20led%20China%20to%20conclude%20that%20India%20did%20not%20have%20the%20political%20will%20to%20escalate%20to%20hot%20war%20beyond%20grey%20zone%20operations.%20Confident%20of%20its%20assessment%2C%20the%20PLA%20may%20have%20ended%20up%20occupying%20nearly%202%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20Indian%20territory%20by%20multiple%20incursions%20in%20east%20Ladakh%20in%20April%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20towards%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20his%20tenure%2C%20Rawat%20made%20the%20case%20of%20how%20his%20continuation%20in%20service%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20CDS%20would%20make%20the%20military%20strong%20and%20resilient%20for%20modern%20warfare.%20This%20was%20a%20good%20reason%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20anoint%20Rawat%20as%20the%20CDS%20with%20a%20three-year%20tenure%20from%20January%202020%20to%20December%202022%20where%20his%20declared%20mandate%20was%20to%20raise%20ITCs%20for%20optimal%20operational%20outcome%20through%20jointness%20and%20synergy%20amongst%20the%20three%20physical%20services%20on%20land%2C%20air%2C%20and%20sea.%20His%20real%20job%20was%20to%20align%20the%20military%20leadership%20(especially%20the%20army%2C%20being%20the%20largest%20of%20the%20three%20services)%20with%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20right-wing%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20accidental%20that%20emulating%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20example%20of%20its%20loyalty%20to%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20(who%20wore%20combat%20fatigue%20in%20his%20two%20roles%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Central%20Military%20Commission%20and%20the%20commander-in-chief)%20rather%20than%20the%20nation%2C%20Modi%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20to%20don%20military%20uniform%20to%20assert%20that%20he%20was%20the%20topmost%20field%20commander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20discharged%20his%20duty%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20senior-most%20commander%20by%20making%20it%20clear%20to%20the%20armed%20forces%20early%20in%20his%20tenure%20that%20its%20focus%20should%20be%20preparedness%2C%20not%20for%20a%20hot%20war%2C%20but%20grey%20zone%20operations%20on%20both%20military%20fronts.%20Grey%20zone%20operations%20terminology%20was%20first%20enunciated%20by%20US%20Special%20Operations%20Forces%20in%202015%20to%20describe%20all%20hostile%20activities%20below%20the%20threshold%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20militaries%2C%20these%20operations%20comprise%20intimidation%2C%20coercion%2C%20and%20cognitive%20confrontation%20by%20non-kinetic%20means%20like%20cyber-attacks%2C%20counter%20space%20capabilities%20for%20satellites%20disablement%2C%20information%20warfare%2C%20cutting%20of%20internet%20subsea%20cables%20and%20so%20on%20with%20the%20only%20rule%20for%20these%20operations%20being%20no%20rules.%20The%20PLA%20calls%20grey%20zone%20operations%20Military%20Operations%20Other%20Than%20War%20(MOOTW).%20It%20has%20refined%20these%20operations%20since%20China%20believes%20that%20they%20help%20in%20negotiations%20with%20an%20adversary%20as%20well%20as%20dent%20his%20will%20to%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20addressing%20his%20first%20combined%20commanders%20conference%20in%20October%202014%2C%20Modi%20told%20the%20military%20leadership%20that%20%E2%80%98the%20threats%20may%20be%20known%2C%20while%20the%20enemy%20may%20be%20invisible.%E2%80%99%20The%20%E2%80%98threat%E2%80%99%20meant%20the%20Pakistan%20military%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98enemy%E2%80%99%20were%20terrorists.%20With%20this%20operational%20directive%2C%20Modi%20formalised%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20counter%20terrorism%20(CT%20ops)%2C%20which%20are%20grey%20zone%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202016%20surgical%20strikes%20qualified%20as%20grey%20zone%20operations%20since%20to%20avoid%20an%20escalation%20into%20war%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuTDYjQ1-cIU%5C%22%3E%20informed%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20before%20it%20announced%20to%20the%20people%20of%20India%20that%20its%20mission%20of%20CT%20ops%20across%20the%20LC%20was%20over.%20Similarly%2C%20when%20the%20Pakistan%20Air%20Force%20reacted%20to%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20Balakot%20strikes%20the%20following%20day%20with%20precision%20air%20attacks%20near%20Indian%20Army%20installations%2C%20the%20IAF%20conceded%20that%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20action%20was%20an%20act%20of%20war%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20objective%20was%20to%20use%20the%20military%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20campaigns.%20Similarly%2C%20during%20the%202017%20Doklam%20crisis%20with%20the%20PLA%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdefence%2Findia-should-play-down-victory-and-be-vigilant-after-disengagement-of-troops-at-doklam%2Farticleshow%2F60282193.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EIndia%20declared%20tactical%20victory%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20latter%20events%20proved%20that%20China%20had%20probably%20outsmarted%20India%20by%20amassing%20thousands%20of%20its%20soldiers%20without%20being%20labelled%20as%20aggressors%20since%20the%20onus%20of%20escalation%20was%20on%20the%20Indian%20Army%20which%20was%20the%20first%20to%20bring%20its%20forces%20close%20to%20the%20LAC.%20Thus%2C%20the%20politicisation%20of%20the%20Indian%20military%20under%20Rawat%20was%20accomplished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20starting%20his%20term%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Fnewsite%2FPrintRelease.aspx%3Frelid%3D197244%5C%22%3ECDS%20on%20January%201%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rawat%20made%20two%20things%20clear%20regarding%20the%20ITCs%3A%20one%2C%20the%20army%20would%20be%20the%20lead%20service%20in%20the%20ITCs.%20And%20two%2C%20the%20IAF%20would%20be%20in%20a%20support%20role%20to%20the%20army.%20Both%20his%20assertions%20betrayed%20his%20poor%20understanding%20of%20modern%20warfare%20where%20the%20PLA%20(identified%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20primary%20threat)%20is%20at%20the%20cutting%20edge%20of%20both%2C%20the%20science%20of%20war%20(technology)%20and%20the%20art%20of%20war%20(war%20concepts).%20It%20also%20remains%20well%20versed%20with%20military%20art%20which%20is%20about%20the%20exploitation%20of%20new%20technologies%20with%20new%20war%20concepts%20for%20optimal%20favourable%20outcome%20in%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECounter-terror%20ops%20detracted%20from%20the%20main%20role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20its%20deep%20involvement%20in%20CT%20ops%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20since%201990%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20lost%20sight%20of%20its%20primary%20task%20of%20preparedness%20for%20hot%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20date%2C%20the%20Indian%20military%20follows%20the%20outdated%20US%20military%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Air-Land%20battle%E2%80%99%20war%20concept%20of%20the%20eighties.%20Given%20two%20war%20domains%20or%20battlespace%20of%20air%20and%20land%2C%20the%20IAF%20and%20the%20army%20focus%20on%20their%20core%20competencies%20for%20war%20while%20coordinating%20their%20war%20plans%20with%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%E2%80%99s%20core%20competencies%20are%20combined%20arms%20operations%20where%20its%20combat%20(infantry%2C%20armour%2C%20engineers)%20and%20combat%20support%20arms%20(artillery)%20complement%20each%20other%20on%20the%20spatial%20battlespace.%20The%20latter%20is%20an%20artificial%20construct%20divided%20into%20tactical%20and%20operational%20level%20with%20the%20focus%20on%20%E2%80%98winning%20the%20first%20battle%E2%80%99.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20core%20competencies%20of%20the%20air%20force%20are%20speed%2C%20range%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20precision%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690464%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20Indian%20army%20soldiers.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FNorthern%20Command-Indian%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20wars%2C%20including%20the%20last%20full-scale%20war%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fa-diplomatic-narrative-of-the-1971-war%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20in%201971%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20air%20force%20was%20in%20support%20of%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20operations%20since%20boots%20on%20the%20ground%20for%20capture%20and%20holding%20of%20territory%20were%20essential.%20The%20winner%20and%20the%20vanquished%20were%20determined%20by%20tactical%20battles%20of%20attrition%20where%20assets%20like%20tanks%2C%20guns%20and%20so%20on%20with%20each%20side%20mattered.%20Victory%20in%20such%20tactical%20wars%20necessitated%20that%20each%20service%20first%20and%20foremost%20concentrates%20on%20its%20core%20competency%20in%20its%20battlespace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20changed%20with%20the%20infusion%20of%20technology%20into%20both%20services%2C%20faster%20in%20the%20IAF%20since%20aviation%20always%20has%20the%20cutting%20edge%20technology%20of%20the%20time.%20So%2C%20by%202000%2C%20the%20IAF%20started%20talking%20of%20strategic%20reach%20with%20its%20limited%20combat%20assets%20implying%20that%20it%20should%20do%20independent%20operations%2C%20and%20not%20be%20tied%20to%20supporting%20army%E2%80%99s%20war%20plans.%20Thus%2C%20it%20was%20natural%20for%20the%20IAF%20to%20not%20accept%20Rawat%E2%80%99s%20archaic%20ITC%20concept%20which%20necessitated%20it%20to%20permanently%20part%20with%20some%20limited%20assets%20to%20commander%20ITC%20or%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20support%20role%20to%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETracking%20the%20competition%3A%20What%20are%20we%20up%20against%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20proceeding%20further%2C%20it%20would%20be%20instructive%20to%20understand%20through%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20military%20art%20why%20India%E2%80%99s%20ITCs%20reform%20was%20outdated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202010%2C%20the%20US%20military%2C%20which%20was%20closely%20watching%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20rise%2C%20concluded%20that%20it%20had%20become%20its%20peer%20competitor.%20By%20the%20infusion%20of%20technology%2C%20the%20PLA%20had%20acquired%20capabilities%20to%20fight%20in%20the%20three%20(two%20virtual%20and%20one%20physical)%20domains%20of%20cyber%2C%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%20and%20outer%20space%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20three%20traditional%20domains%20of%20land%2C%20air%20and%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECapability%20to%20fight%20in%20a%20domain%20meant%20the%20ability%20to%20combat%2C%20confront%20and%20compete%20as%20well%20as%20manage%20the%20best%20options%20in%20it%20against%20a%20peer%20adversary.%20This%20is%20distinct%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98force%20multiplier%E2%80%99%20which%2C%20as%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20boost%20fighting%20capability%20in%20an%20existing%20domain%20like%20land%2C%20air%20and%20sea.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20China%20also%20became%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20shipbuilding%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20in%20the%20traditional%20domains%2C%20the%20PLA%20had%20shifted%20the%20focus%20to%20areas%20which%20for%20lack%20of%20technology%20were%20unexploited%20earlier.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20the%20air%20domain%20(up%20to%2020km%20altitude%20from%20ground)%20where%20fighter%20aircraft%20and%20drones%20could%20fly%2C%20the%20PLA%20created%20a%20new%20space%20called%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fscience%2Farticle%2F3241059%2Ffifth-force-china-adding-hypersonic-near-space-command-its-military-precise-and-merciless-attacks%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98near%20space%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%2020km%20to%20100km%20altitude%20above%20ground%20beyond%20which%20%E2%80%98outer%20space%E2%80%99%20was%20used%20by%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98near%20space%E2%80%99%20was%20to%20be%20exploited%20by%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20hypersonic%20cruise%20missiles%20and%20hypersonic%20glide%20vehicles%2C%20a%20capability%20the%20US%20military%20lacked.%20Similarly%2C%20in%20the%20sea%20domain%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98deep%20sea%E2%80%99%20at%20depth%20of%20300meters%20and%20below%20was%20to%20be%20preferred%20for%20war%20fighting%20with%20sea%20drones%20and%20submarines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20assumed%20power%20in%20November%202012%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20roll%20out%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%20across%20Eurasia%2C%20Africa%2C%20Latin%20America%2C%20and%20Oceania-Pacific%20islands.%20This%20required%20the%20PLA%20to%20take%20on%20two%20additional%20roles%3A%20protect%20Chinese%20assets%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20interests%20in%20the%20BRI%20nation%2C%20and%20create%20deterrence%20for%20safety%20of%20its%20commercial%20trade%20through%20the%20Sea%20Lanes%20of%20Communications%20across%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20region.%20China%20is%20also%20determined%20to%20re-unite%20claimed%20Taiwan%20and%20Tibet%20with%20the%20mainland.%20The%20latter%20refers%20to%20south%20Tibet%20or%20the%20Indian%20state%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20And%20after%20India%20created%20the%20Union%20Territory%20of%20Ladakh%20following%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20China%20announced%20that%20Indian%20Ladakh%20being%20part%20of%20the%20Aksai%20Chin%20also%20belongs%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20added%20PLA%20tasks%20and%20its%20grown%20capabilities%20necessitated%20development%20of%20new%20war%20concepts%20along%20with%20appropriate%20structural%20reforms%20to%20optimise%20its%20war%20outcome.%20So%2C%20in%202014%2C%20the%20PLA%20announced%20its%20new%20military%20strategy%20with%20three%20highlights%3A%20Three%20new%20war%20domains%20of%20cyber%2C%20outer%20space%2C%20and%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%3B%20naval%20warfare%3B%20and%20the%20concept%20of%20Joint%20Integrated%20Operations%20(JIO).%20In%20the%20JIO%2C%20the%20PLA%20decided%20not%20to%20follow%20the%20US%20military%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98joint%20force%E2%80%99%20(which%20is%20being%20blindly%20emulated%20by%20Indian%20military%20as%20part%20of%20ITCs)%20but%20to%20create%20%E2%80%98mission%20sets%E2%80%99%3A%20strike%20packages%20specific%20to%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fover-ambition-half-baked-ideas-military-integrated-theatre-commands%5C%22%3EOver-Ambition%20and%20Half-Baked%20Ideas%20Plague%20the%20Military%E2%80%99s%20Plan%20for%20Integrated%20Theatre%20Commands%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20structural%20changes%2C%20after%20three%20years%20deliberations%2C%20the%20PLA%20announced%20in%202015%20military%20reforms%20where%20Western%20Theatre%20Command%20(WTC)%20was%20raised%20specifically%20for%20war%20with%20India.%20These%20reforms%20were%20to%20be%20accomplished%20in%20five%20years%2C%20that%20is%2C%202020%2C%20the%20year%20it%20occupied%20Indian%20territory%20in%20east%20Ladakh.%20In%20four%20years%20since%2C%20the%20PLA%20has%20collected%20data%20and%20identified%20targets%20in%20combat%20space%20and%20the%20whole-of-nation%20to%20unleash%20its%20doctrine%20called%20%E2%80%98systems%20destruction%20warfare%E2%80%99.%20China%2C%20today%2C%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20shut%20down%20Indian%20civilian%20life%20as%20well%20as%20destroy%20communications%20(the%20lifeline%20of%20command%20and%20control)%20in%20the%20combat%20zone%20or%20battlespace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20unlike%20the%20Indian%20military%20which%20talks%20of%20a%20border%20war%20with%20China%20on%20the%20LAC%2C%20the%20PLA%20has%20prepared%20for%20a%20war%20of%20sovereignty%20to%20wrest%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Ladakh%20from%20India.%20Not%20prepared%20for%20an%20occupation%20war%20by%20China%2C%20the%20Indian%20military%20has%20instead%20conflated%20it%20with%20grey%20zone%20operations%20on%20the%20LAC.%20Following%20the%20worst%20grey%20zone%20operations%20in%20recent%20memory%20on%20June%2015%202020%20in%20the%20Galwan%20valley%20where%20Indian%20army%20lost%2020%20soldiers%20with%20hundreds%20made%20prisoners%20by%20the%20PLA%2C%20Indian%20military%20leadership%20has%20told%20the%20nation%20that%20it%20has%20done%20re-balancing%20of%20forces%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20front%20to%20the%20LAC%20to%20take%20on%20the%20PLA%20challenge.%20The%20added%20benefit%20for%20the%20army%20leadership%20in%20believing%20that%20a%20border%20war%20with%20China%20is%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%20is%20that%20it%20continues%20to%20retain%20its%20status%20as%20lead%20service%20for%20a%20border%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrey%20zone%20ops%20being%20prioritised%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cue%20for%20military%20leadership%20to%20focus%20on%20grey%20zone%20operations%20on%20the%20LAC%20has%20come%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20who%20in%20September%202022%20told%20the%20Russian%20President%20Putin%20that%20%E2%80%98this%20was%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war%2C%E2%80%99%20notwithstanding%20that%20it%20is%20the%20opposite%20of%20it.%20In%20great%20power%20contestation%20where%20the%20global%20geopolitics%20has%20shifted%20from%20Europe%20to%20Asia%20Pacific%20with%20US%E2%80%99%20superpower%20status%20under%20challenge%20by%20China%20and%20Russia%2C%20the%20world%20has%20entered%20the%20unprecedented%20phase%20of%20wars%2C%20struggles%2C%20and%20strategic%20competition%20to%20reshape%20the%20world%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20since%20grey%20zone%20operations%20are%20manpower%20heavy%20as%20on%20the%20LC%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20every%20bit%20of%20Indian%20territory%20on%20the%20LAC%20must%20be%20guarded%20against%20enemy%20transgressions%20and%20incursions.%20Hence%2C%20the%20army%20is%20on%20a%20spree%20to%20raise%20new%20formations.%20The%20latest%20is%20the%20raising%20of%2018%20corps%20(which%20has%20under%20it%20a%20division%20and%20three%20independent%20brigades)%20in%20February%20this%20year%20for%20guarding%20the%20middle%20sector%20in%20states%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%20now%20has%20seven%20corps%20(namely%2C%2014%2C%2018%2C%2033%2C%203%2C%204%2C%201%2C%20and%2017)%20on%20the%20LAC%2C%20with%20two%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%201%20and%2017%20corps%20%E2%80%94%20called%20strike%20corps.%20Never%20mind%20that%20(a)%20land%20domain%20will%20have%20minimum%20role%20in%20war%20with%20the%20PLA%2C%20and%20(b)%20strike%20corps%20with%20counterattack%20capability%20will%20be%20meaningless%20against%20China%20which%20will%20start%20and%20end%20the%20war%20by%20total%20domination%20of%20strategic%20and%20operational%20levels%20of%20war.%20Once%20this%20is%20done%2C%20the%20PLA%20has%20AI%20powered%20drones%20with%20facial%20recognition%20systems%20to%20take%20out%20hundreds%20and%20thousands%20of%20Indian%20soldiers%20with%20their%20communication%20potentially%20snapped%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20since%20China%20has%20vibrant%20defence-industrial%20complex%2C%20it%20would%20have%20prepared%20required%20land-based%20missiles%20under%20its%20organisation%20called%20Rocket%20Force%2C%20and%20long-range%20precision%20artillery%20to%20threaten%20identified%20Indian%20targets%20with%20intense%20rates%20of%20salvos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%20to%20ITCs%2C%20they%20are%20of%20little%20help%20when%20the%20Indian%20military%20has%20limited%20assets%2C%20imports%20specialised%20ammunitions%2C%20has%20a%20frugal%20inventory%20of%20land-based%20missiles%2C%20and%20importantly%2C%20it%20has%20capability%20to%20combat%20only%20in%20three%20physical%20war%20domains.%20Without%20domain%20capabilities%20in%20cyberspace%20and%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%20no%20modern%20war%20can%20be%20won.%20Thus%2C%20the%20need%20is%20to%20study%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98systems%20destruction%20warfare%E2%80%99%2C%20create%20new%20war%20domains%20instead%20of%20seeking%20force%20multipliers%2C%20and%20for%20the%20military%20leadership%20to%20understand%20that%20politicisation%20undermines%20war-preparedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpravin-sawhney%5C%22%3EPravin%20Sawhney%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20the%20author%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Last%20War%3A%20How%20AI%20Will%20Shape%20India%E2%80%99s%20Final%20Showdown%20With%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709904558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06155517%2FEffect-14-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fchallenges-for-the-army-politicisation-prioritising-counter-insurgency-and-a-modernising-adversary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20has%20recently%20announced%20its%20defence%20budget%2C%20which%20conceals%20the%20actual%20extent%20to%20which%20India%E2%80%99s%20neighbour%20has%20gone%20about%20modernising%20its%20armed%20forces.%20India%20has%20seen%20politicisation%20of%20its%20services%20and%20priorities%20which%20make%20its%20tasks%20tougher.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fchallenges-for-the-army-politicisation-prioritising-counter-insurgency-and-a-modernising-adversary%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22France%20inscribes%20the%20right%20to%20abortion%20in%20its%20constitution%20as%20world%20marks%20International%20Women's%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709904368000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108332314%2Cimgsize-1787362.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrance-inscribes-the-right-to-abortion-in-its-constitution-as-world-marks-international-womens-day%2Farticleshow%2F108332289.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108332