al%20Conference%20(NC)%20vice%20president%20Omar%20Abdullah%20here%20on%20Friday%20said%20personal%20attacks%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20backfire%20for%20the%20opposition%20and%20slogans%20about%20his%20family%20only%20secure%20a%20%26quot%3Bself-goal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20Abdullah's%20remarks%20came%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20about%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav's%20jibe%20on%20the%20prime%20minister%20for%20having%20no%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20Abdullah%2C%20whose%20party%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20opposition's%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20said%20such%20things%20backfire%20like%20the%20%26quot%3BChowkidar%20chor%20hai%26quot%3B%20slogan%20did%20in%20the%20last%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20never%20in%20favour%20of%20such%20slogans%20and%20nor%20they%20benefit%20us.%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20is%20an%20opposite%20effect%20when%20we%20use%20such%20slogans%2C%20it%20causes%20loss%20to%20us.%20A%20voter%20is%20not%20satisfied%20with%20these%20slogans%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20know%20how%20the%20issues%20he%20faces%20today%20would%20be%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20wants%20to%20know%20about%20employment%20generation%2C%20tackling%20agricultural%20distress%2C%20reactivate%20rural%20economy.%20He%20wants%20to%20hear%20about%20those%20things%20rather%20than%20whether%20someone%20has%20a%20family%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20chief%20minister%20said%20the%20opposition%20only%20secures%20a%20self-goal%20with%20such%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20we%20have%20given%20him%20(Modi)%20an%20open%20goal%20post%20and%20he%20has%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20his%20advantage%20by%20saying%20that%20Modi%20belongs%20to%20those%20who%20do%20not%20have%20anyone.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20any%20answer%20to%20that%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20only%20say%20that%20we%20should%20not%20indulge%20in%20such%20personal%20politics%20but%20raise%20the%20issues%20of%20the%20public.%20Chowkidar%2C%20Rafale%2C%20Parivar%20--%20these%20do%20not%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20about%20the%20National%20Conference%20not%20leaving%20any%20seat%20in%20the%20valley%20for%20the%20PDP%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said%20the%20situation%20has%20kept%20the%20PDP%20out%2C%20not%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PDP%20came%20at%20the%20third%20number%20in%20the%20last%20Parliament%20elections%20and%20how%20is%20it%20justified%20that%20the%20number%20one%20or%20number%20two%20party%20will%20leave%20the%20claim%20on%20the%20seat%20and%20give%20it%20to%20the%20third%20number%3F%20Also%2C%20I%20do%20not%20see%20any%20influence%20of%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20seat%20(south%20Kashmir-Rajouri)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20coalition%20is%20concerned%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said%2C%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20every%20party%20to%20keep%20the%20coalition%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20ask%20us%20about%20the%20seats%20for%20them%2C%20but%20when%20they%20target%20the%20National%20Conference%20through%20their%20tweets%20or%20on%20social%20media%2C%20then%20you%20don't%20ask%20them%20if%20that%20is%20the%20coalition%20dharma...%20The%20NC%20is%20attacked%20even%20when%20elections%20take%20place%20in%20Pakistan.%20They%20said%20on%20Twitter%20that%20what%20happened%20in%20Pakistan%20elections%2C%20reminded%20the%20people%20of%20what%20happened%20here%20in%201987%20elections.%20What%20coalition%20dharma%20is%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20know%20under%20what%20influence%20did%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20target%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20but%20the%20PDP%20forced%20itself%20into%20that%20as%20well%20and%20attacked%20the%20NC.%20They%20along%20with%20Azad%20attacked%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20and%20the%20NC%20from%20their%20Twitter%20platform%20and%20you%20ask%20us%20where%20is%20the%20coalition%20dharma%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20despite%20the%20PDP's%20attacks%20on%20his%20party%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20has%20told%20the%20Congress%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20keep%20doors%20open%20for%20an%20alliance%20for%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20first%20we%20will%20see%20their%20(PDP's)%20approach%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20Parliamentary%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference%20vice%20president%20said%20his%20party%20has%20discussed%20the%20seat%20sharing%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20national%20party%20would%20contest%20from%20two%20seats%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20told%20them%20to%20field%20their%20candidates%20from%20Udhampur%20and%20Jammu%20seats.%20We%20have%20also%20told%20them%20that%20the%20NC%20will%20not%20field%20its%20candidate%20on%20the%20Ladakh%20seat%2C%20but%20our%20endeavour%20should%20be%20to%20field%20a%20consensus%20candidate%20there%20who%20can%20take%20back%20the%20seat%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20said%20had%20he%20known%20before%20joining%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20%26quot%3Bweaken%26quot%3B%20his%20party%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20some%20other%20member%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20%26quot%3Bthen%20perhaps%20I%20would%20never%20have%20joined%20the%20alliance%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709901240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-06%2F3b49lj2o_omar-abdullah_625x30