C%20empires%2C%20states%2C%20and%20governments%20were%20formed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20we%20still%20continue%20to%20take%20utmost%20care%20of%20our%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYour%20coming%20has%20ushered%20in%20a%20sense%20of%20great%20festivity%20as%20we%20see%20hundreds%20of%20armed%20police%20personnel%20moving%20around%20the%20area.%20It%20feels%20like%20we%20are%20in%20an%20Orwellian%20act.%20Would%20that%20be%20the%20norm%20for%20our%20future%3F%20They%20are%20frisking%20people%20and%20putting%20up%20roadblocks%20and%20barricades%20in%20many%20places.%20It%20seems%20%3Cspan%3Elike%3C%2Fspan%3E%20it%20is%20becoming%20a%20norm%20as%20we%20see%20different%20flag%20marches%20by%20police%20and%20commandos%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20television%20channels%20air%20them%20with%20much%20pride%20and%20pomp%20as%20if%20it%20is%20something%20good.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20wonder%20why%20not%20much%20of%20the%20camera%20goes%20to%20the%20other%20side%20where%20people%20could%20express%20their%20anguish%20of%20forceful%20displacement%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fstatic%2Fkaziranga-rhino-poaching%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20human%20rights%20violations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20also%20take%20place%20in%20Kaziranga.%20However%2C%20we%20keep%20hearing%20that%20in%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20everything%20is%20rosy%20and%20bright.%20Perhaps%20we%20have%20no%20idea%20of%20what%20it%20is%20as%20we%20rarely%20see%20much%20of%20what%20the%20developed%20and%20rich%20world%20looks%20like.%20We%20are%20happy%20that%20if%20you%20take%20a%20keen%20look%2C%20you%20will%20see%20what%20rich%20land%20with%20poor%20people%20looks%20like%20due%20to%20lopsided%20development%20for%20a%20few.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20chief%20minister%2C%20Dr.%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20seemed%20exuberant%20about%20your%20visit.%20He%20has%20taken%20the%20onus%20of%20saying%20out%20loud%20that%20his%20government%20has%20brought%20a%20prime%20minister%20to%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20the%20biodiversity.%20Hopefully%2C%20the%20golden%20tiger%2C%20that%20our%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20boasting%20about%2C%20will%20give%20a%20sighting%20to%20our%20royal%20guest.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20rumour%20that%20you%20would%20be%20staying%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvaanigreens.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVaani%20Greens%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20place%20specially%20curated%20by%20our%20honourable%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20family.%20We%20are%20often%20enticed%20by%20the%20beautiful%20pictures%20that%20come%20out%20of%20the%20sprawling%20tea%20garden%20and%20the%20cottages%20that%20look%20like%20igloos%2C%20set%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20an%20animal%20corridor.%20The%20media%20also%20keeps%20saying%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthecrosscurrent.in%2Fkanchanjuri_03_03_2023%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eit%E2%80%99s%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Kanchanjuri%20Animal%20Corridor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20the%20powerful%20to%20decide%2C%20who%20are%20we%3F%20Oh%2C%20the%20irony%20of%20our%20times%2C%20people%20are%20gossip-mongers%20and%20we%20know%20that%20you%20would%20be%20staying%20in%20a%20government%20property%20in%20Kohora%20%E2%80%93%20the%20epicentre%20of%20tourism%20in%20Kaziranga.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERespected%20prime%20minister%2C%20we%20wish%20you%20could%20stay%20in%20the%20Grand%20Hyatt%20hotel%2C%20which%20is%20being%20built%20on%20Adivasi%2Ftea%20tribe%20land%20without%20any%20form%20of%20consultation%20or%20compensation.%20We%20are%20also%20confused%20about%20how%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20with%20120%20rooms%20can%20be%20built%20on%20farmlands%20which%20were%20also%20used%20by%20elephants%20as%20their%20corridor.%20We%20are%20concerned%20about%20what%20is%20happening%20behind%20your%20back.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20accomplice%2C%20the%20health%20minister%20of%20Assam%2C%20share%20boundaries%20of%20their%20huge%20gated%20and%20fenced%20properties%20in%20Kaziranga%2C%20but%20we%2C%20the%20poor%20and%20unwanted%2C%20are%20finding%20it%20difficult%20to%20protect%20our%20legal%20rights%20to%20the%20little%20lands%20that%20we%20cultivate%20to%20feed%20ourselves%20and%20the%20wild%20animals%20of%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20and%20Tiger%20Reserve.%20This%20is%20not%20fair%2C%20what%20they%20are%20doing%20to%20you%20%E2%80%93%20who%20claims%20with%20such%20pride%20that%20there%20will%20be%20zero%20tolerance%20against%20illegalities%20and%20also%20the%20famous%20phrases%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENa%20khaunga%2C%20na%20khaane%20doonga%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9CSab%20ka%20saath%20sab%20ka%20vikas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20tourism%20minister%2C%20Jayanta%20Malla%20Baruah%2C%20has%20talked%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20your%20visit%20which%20would%20help%20Kaziranga%20in%20its%20promotion.%20We%20wonder%20what%20more%20could%20come%20up%20into%20the%20UNESCO%20site.%20Kaziranga%20has%20seen%20every%20inch%20of%20farm%20and%20fallow%20land%20being%20gradually%20swallowed%20by%20big%20hotel%20chains%20like%20the%20Grand%20Hyatt%2C%20Taj%20Hotels%2C%20Vaani%20Greens%2C%20IORA%2C%20Borgos%2C%20Mandu%2C%20Royal%20de%20Casa%2C%20etc.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20people%20complaining%20about%20how%20the%20farmlands%20are%20being%20changed%20into%20commercial%20plots%20overnight%2C%20though%20there%20is%20a%20strict%20forest%20department%20and%20revenue%20office%20which%20are%20supposed%20to%20safeguard%20the%20land.%20And%20how%20hills%20have%20been%20flattened%20and%20walls%20built%2C%20that%20have%20killed%20perennial%20streams%20and%20lakes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOh%20dear%20prime%20minister%2C%20we%20would%20want%20you%20to%20come%20and%20sit%20in%20a%20mud%20or%20a%20bamboo%20stilt%20house%20in%20some%20village%20like%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F977999%2Fas-kaziranga-national-park-spreads-local-residents-tear-down-their-homes-before-they-are-evicted%2523%3A~%3Atext%3DEvictions%252520in%252520Kaziranga%252520usually%252520attract%2Cvoluntarily%2525E2%252580%25259D%252520tore%252520down%252520their%252520homes.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Hatikhuli%20Borbil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Its%20residents%20have%20been%20living%20there%20for%20generations%20and%20suddenly%2C%20one%20fine%20day%2C%20the%20forest%20department%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20their%20land.%20Now%20they%20are%20facing%20eviction%20without%20any%20form%20of%20rehabilitation.%20Does%20that%20sound%20fair%20to%20you%3F%20You%2C%20as%20a%20universal%20leader%2C%20surely%20know%20that%20indigenous%20communities%20are%20the%20best%20wardens%20of%20the%20land%20and%20forest.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPardon%20us%2C%20apart%20from%20our%20uncertain%20future%2C%20we%20would%20want%20to%20feed%20you%20with%20the%20best%20foraged%20vegetables%2C%20Namsing%20(fermented%20fish)%2C%20Apong%2FHariya%20(used%20for%20rituals)%2C%20fermented%20drinks%20that%20keep%20our%20ancestors%20and%20us%20happy%20and%20connected%2C%20and%20show%20you%20our%20ecologically%20sensible%20and%20frugal%20living.%20We%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20have%20you%2C%20the%20way%20you%20have%20done%20before%20every%20election%2C%20visiting%20some%20Dalit%20households%20in%20mainland%20India.%20Our%20poor%20evicted%20villagers%20of%20Kaziranga%20would%20also%20take%20great%20pride%20if%20you%20would%20come%20to%20sit%20in%20our%20humble%20dwellings%20squatting%20over%20roads%20and%20embankments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20hope%20your%20security%20is%20tight%20enough%20as%20we%20see%20barricades%20and%20flag%20marches%20too.%20We%20are%20well-surveilled%2C%20too%2C%20with%20the%20patrolling%20commandos%20and%20special%20task%20forces%20who%20spend%20all%20their%20time%20in%20the%20civilian%20areas%20rather%20than%20the%20forest%20areas.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20ask%20how%20our%20villagers%20are%20scared%20to%20even%20venture%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20as%20there%20have%20been%20so%20many%20incidents%20where%20they%20have%20been%20thrashed%20by%20those%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fkaziranga-bbc-shoot-poaching%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egun-wielding%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20forest%20guards%20under%20mere%20suspicion.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOh%2C%20did%20you%20know%2C%20the%20forest%20guards%20here%20enjoy%20great%20powers%20to%20use%20their%20guns%20which%20they%20say%20can%20shoot%20at%20the%20sight%20of%20anyone%20inside%20the%20park%20boundaries%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20if%20we%20poor%20people%20knew%20the%20boundaries%2C%20as%20Kaziranga%20started%20with%20around%20300%20sq%20km%20area%20and%20today%20it%20boasts%20of%20more%20than%201%2C100%20km%20territory%2C%20so%20tell%20us%20whose%20mathematics%20is%20going%20wrong.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20understand%20the%20presence%20of%20so%20many%20police%20and%20military%20when%20you%20are%20here%2C%20but%20why%20does%20Kaziranga%20have%20such%20high%20security%20in%20civilian%20areas%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20and%20it%20is%20only%20increasing.%20Some%20people%20say%20it%20is%20a%20colonial%20hangover%20as%20the%20forest%20department%20is%20one%20institution%20that%20has%20not%20changed%20much%20since.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20so%20much%20that%20we%20would%20like%20to%20share%20but%20only%20if%20there%20was%20time%20for%20you%20to%20listen%20to%20our%20elders%20about%20the%20unbroken%20history%20of%20broken%20promises.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20bid%20you%20farewell%2C%20let%20history%20judge%20itself%2C%20while%20we%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20survive%2C%20maintain%20sanity%20and%20dignity%2C%20and%20bring%20in%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWarm%20regards%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPranab%20Doley%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EPranab%20Doley%20is%20a%20youth%20leader%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20community%20of%20Bokakhat%20displaced%20by%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709901051000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F08122740%2FDAvKGMrV0AEbHas.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fto-the-pm-from-kaziranga-an-open-letter-decrying-displacement-human-rights-violations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20Assam%20with%20his%20arrival%20at%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20scheduled%20for%20March%208.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fto-the-pm-from-kaziranga-an-open-letter-decrying-displacement-human-rights-violations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22High%20Salaries%2C%20PR%20Visas%3A%20How%20Indians%20Were%20Duped%20Into%20Fighting%20Russia's%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI's%20raids%20on%20agents%20and%20companies%20involved%20in%20trafficking%20Indians%20to%20Russia%20have%20revealed%20the%20nefarious%20ways%20in%20which%20youngsters%20were%20duped%20into%20fighting%20the%20country's%20wars%20against%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20were%20sent%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20being%20given%20jobs%20as%20delivery%20boys%2C%20others%20were%20told%20they%20would%20be%20working%20as%20helpers%20for%20the%20Russian%20army%2C%20but%20were%20categorically%20assured%20that%20their%20duties%20would%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20frontlines.%20The%20youngsters%20were%20also%20told%20that%20since%20Russia%20needs%20manpower%20in%20the%20war%20effort%2C%20the%20country%20would%20issue%20a%20%26quot%3Bgovernment%20official%26quot%3B%20card%20to%20them%2C%20which%20would%20all%20but%20guarantee%20a%20permanent%20residency%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agents'%20lies%20have%20been%20exposed%20not%20just%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20at%20least%20one%20man%20from%20Hyderabad%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20died%20in%20the%20fighting%2C%20but%20also%20by%20the%20CBI's%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20the%20companies%2C%20which%20states%20that%20some%20Indians%20were%20also%20grievously%20injured%20in%20the%20warzone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20briefing%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20trafficking%20and%20the%20risks%20involved.%20%26quot%3BSeveral%20Indian%20nationals%20have%20been%20duped%20into%20working%20with%20the%20Russian%20Army...%20We%20once%20again%20appeal%20to%20Indian%20nationals%20to%20not%20be%20swayed%20by%20offers%20made%20by%20agents%20for%20support%20jobs%20with%20the%20Russian%20Army.%20This%20is%20fraught%20with%20danger%20and%20risk%20to%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeaving%20Dreams%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI's%20FIR%20names%2017%20agents%20and%20companies%20but%20NDTV's%20conversations%20with%20the%20families%20of%20trafficked%20youngsters%20have%20revealed%20that%20one%20of%20the%20key%20movers%20and%20shakers%20was%20Dubai-based%20Faizan%20Khan%20aka%20Baba%2C%20who%20ran%20a%20popular%20YouTube%20channel%20called%20'Baba%20Vlogs'.%20Khan%20is%20also%20named%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20his%20videos%20on%20the%20channel%2C%20Khan%20is%20seen%20in%20St%20Petersburg%2C%20Russia.%20He%20begins%20the%20video%20by%20pointing%20out%20how%20Finland%20and%20Estonia%20are%20less%20than%20150%20km%20away%20from%20the%20city%20and%20says%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20understand%20when%20you%20are%20so%20close%2C%20in%20hushed%20words%2C%20the%20things%20you%20can%20do%20when%20you%20get%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShowing%20his%20viewers%20how%20beautiful%20St%20Petersburg%20is%20and%20how%20far%20it%20is%20from%20the%20fighting%2C%20Khan%20goes%20on%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20jobs%20available%20as%20delivery%20boys%20and%20also%20as%20helpers%20with%20the%20Russian%20army.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20join%20as%20helpers%2C%20it%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20fire%20a%20cannon%20or%20guns%20or%20go%20to%20the%20frontlines.%20Once%20the%20army%20has%20crossed%20an%20area%2C%20your%20job%20will%20be%20to%20empty%20buildings%2C%20get%20stuff%20out%2C%20or%20guard%20ammunition.%20Your%20job%20will%20be%20as%20a%20helper%20or%20a%20security%20guard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20tells%20the%20youngsters%20that%20they%20will%20be%20given%20training%20for%20three%20months%2C%20during%20which%20they%20will%20be%20paid%20Rs%2040%2C000%20each%20month%2C%20which%20will%20increase%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh%20a%20month%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20advantage%20is%20that%20you%20will%20get%20a%20government%20official%20card.%20You%20will%20stay%20in%20a%20nice%20place%20and%20get%20decent%20food.%20You%20will%20get%20priority%20everywhere.%20Based%20on%20that%20card%2C%20you%20can%20get%20Schengen%20visas%2C%20go%20to%20some%20other%20country%20or%20get%20a%20PR%20visa.%20The%20government's%20thinking%20is%20that%20if%20you%20support%20them%20now%2C%20they%20will%20also%20give%20you%20a%20benefit%2C%20they%20will%20give%20you%20a%20PR%20visa%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20any%20danger%20or%20you%20had%20to%20be%20on%20the%20frontlines%2C%20even%20I%20would%20not%20have%20done%20this.%20I%20have%20confirmed%20everything%20personally.%20You%20will%20be%20my%20responsibility%20and%20if%20you%20had%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20war%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20me%20too.%20You%20will%20not%20be%20on%20the%20border%2C%20you%20will%20just%20have%20to%20help%20the%20Army%2C%26quot%3B%20Khan%20assured%20his%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fee%20for%20all%20this%2C%20the%20agent%20said%2C%20would%20be%20Rs%203%20lakh%20and%20his%20team%20would%20pick%20people%20up%20from%20the%20airport%20and%20help%20them%20with%20everything.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20exactly%20how%20Mohammed%20Asfan%2C%20the%2030-year-old%20Hyderabadi%20man%20whose%20death%20was%20confirmed%20in%20the%20fighting%20against%20Ukraine%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20was%20fooled.%20His%20family%20said%20he%20and%20two%20of%20his%20friends%20had%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20Khan%20and%20they%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20Russia%20after%20being%20promised%20jobs%20as%20helpers%20in%20government%20offices%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECBI's%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20which%20carried%20out%20raids%20in%20seven%20cities%20-%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20Ambala%2C%20Chandigarh%20and%20Madurai%20-%20on%20Thursday%2C%20and%20also%20registered%20a%20case%2C%20has%20mentioned%20in%20its%20FIR%20that%20other%20agents%20also%20used%20a%20similar%20playbook.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20above%20accused%20persons%20themselves%2C%20and%20through%20their%20agents%2C%20trafficked%20Indian%20nationals%20to%20Russia%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20getting%20jobs%20related%20to%20Russian%20Army%20(as)%20security%20guards%2C%20helper%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FIR%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20it%20has%20been%20learnt%20that%20on%20reaching%20Russia%2C%20passports%20of%20these%20Indian%20Nationals%20were%20taken%2Fsnatched%20by%20agents%20at%20Russia.%20They%20were%20being%20trained%20in%20combat%20roles%20and%20provided%20with%20Russian%20army%20uniform%20and%20batches.%20Thereafter%2C%20these%20Indian%20Nationals%20are%2Fwere%20being%20deployed%20at%20front%20bases%20in%20Russia%20-%20Ukraine%20War%20Zone%20against%20their%20wishes%20and%20put%20their%20lives%20in%20grave%20danger.%20It%20has%20been%20ascertained%20that%20some%20human%20trafficking%20victims%20were%20also%20got%20grievously%20injured%20in%20the%20war%20zone%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20has%20said%20in%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20also%20mentioned%20that%20many%20Indians%20were%20being%20taken%20on%20education%20visas%20by%20promising%20them%20admission%20to%20%26quot%3Bdubious%26quot%3B%20private%20universities%20in%20Russia.%20%26quot%3BThereafter%2C%20they%20are%20left%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20visa%20agents%20and%20college%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709900940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F00m6qoqc_mohammed-asfan_625x300_07_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmohammed-asfan-indian-killed-in-russia-high-salaries-pr-visas-how-indians-were-duped-into-fighting-russias-war-5200866%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CBI's%20raids%20on%20agents%20and%20companies%20involved%20in%20trafficking%20Indians%20to%20Russia%20have%20revealed%20the%20nefarious%20ways%20in%20which%20youngsters%20were%20duped%20into%20fighting%20the%20country's%20wars%20against%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmohammed-asfan-indian-killed-in-russia-high-salaries-pr-visas-how-indians-were-duped-into-fighting-russias-war-5200866%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmohammed-asfan-indian-killed-in-russia-high-salaries-pr-visas-how-