%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20poised%20to%20witness%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20due%20to%20the%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fai-elections-and-law-india-eu-talks-underline-why-collective-action-is-important-5099192%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20on%20a%20large%20scale%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-ai-pm-dubbed-speeches-eye-on-mission-370-bjp-dubs-pms-speeches-in-8-languages-in-real-time-5187279%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20established%20itself%20as%20a%20frontrunner%20in%20adopting%20cutting-edge%20technology%20compared%20to%20other%20political%20factions%20in%20India.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20leading%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20stands%20out%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20tech-savvy%20leaders%20in%20the%20nation.%20In%20preparation%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20employed%20AI%20to%20translate%20PM%20Modi's%20speeches%20into%20eight%20different%20languages%2C%20aiming%20to%20expand%20his%20reach%20across%20diverse%20linguistic%20communities.%20These%20speeches%20are%20now%20accessible%20in%20Bengali%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Tamil%2C%20Telugu%2C%20Punjabi%2C%20Marathi%2C%20Odia%2C%20and%20Malayalam%20through%20various%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20PM%20Modi%20utilised%20AI%20to%20translate%20his%20live%20speech%20during%20the%20Kashi%20Tamil%20Sangamam%20event%20in%20Varanasi%20in%20December%202023.%20Addressing%20the%20audience%20in%20Hindi%2C%20his%20speech%20was%20seamlessly%20translated%20into%20Tamil%20in%20real-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Approach%20More%20Advanced%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20note%20that%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20actively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeta-forms-teams-to-combat-election-disinformation-ai-threat-ai-abuse-in-eu-elections-5128757%5C%22%3Eharnessing%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20enhance%20their%20campaign%20strategies.%20However%2C%20current%20assessments%20suggest%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20adopted%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20approach.%20The%20BJP's%20decision%20to%20translate%20speeches%20into%20these%20eight%20languages%20strategically%20aims%20to%20broaden%20its%20electoral%20footprint%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Punjab%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Telangana.%20These%20eight%20states%20collectively%20account%20for%20228%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20Indian%20elections%2C%C2%A0Vinay%20Deshpande%2C%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20Rajneethi%2C%20a%20political%20management%20consultant%20firm%2C%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CAI's%20role%20in%20elections%20in%20India%20spans%20the%20entire%20spectrum%20of%20campaign%20strategies%2C%20from%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20voter%20identification%20to%20the%20complex%20nuances%20of%20content%20creation%20and%20delivery.%20By%20enabling%20a%20more%20data-driven%2C%20targeted%2C%20and%20efficient%20approach%2C%20AI%20is%20setting%20new%20standards%20for%20how%20political%20campaigns%20are%20conducted%20in%20the%20digital%20age.%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETargeting%20Voters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20aid%20of%20AI%2C%20political%20parties%20and%20their%20leaders%20can%20now%20target%20voters%20with%20precision.%20This%20is%20achieved%20by%20leveraging%20extensive%20datasets%2C%20including%20population%20analysis%2C%20social%20media%20engagement%2C%20and%20online%20behaviour.%20The%20profiles%20serve%20as%20the%20foundation%20for%20delivering%20personalized%20content%2C%20advertisements%2C%20and%20messages%20tailored%20to%20resonate%20with%20their%20unique%20interests%20and%20concerns.%20Unlike%20traditional%20campaigning%20methods%2C%20AI-powered%20micro-targeting%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20more%20effective%20in%20influencing%20voter%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20benefits%20of%20AI%20in%20the%20elections%2C%C2%A0Divyendra%20Singh%20Jadoun%2C%20founder%20of%20Polymath%20Solution%2C%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CAI%20can%20automate%20routine%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20data%20entry%20and%20communication%2C%20allowing%20campaign%20staff%20to%20focus%20on%20more%20strategic%20activities.%20It%20can%20analyse%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%20to%20identify%20trends%20and%20patterns%20in%20voter%20behaviour%2C%20helping%20political%20parties%20optimise%20their%20campaign%20strategies.%20AI%20can%20also%20provide%20real-time%20analytics%20on%20campaign%20performance%2C%20allowing%20parties%20to%20make%20data-driven%20decisions%20to%20improve%20their%C2%A0strategies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2023%2C%20supporters%20of%20the%20late%20former%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20Karunanidhi%20witnessed%20his%20AI-generated%20revival%20at%20the%20book%20release%20event%20of%20fellow%20DMK%20politician%20T.R.%20Baalu.%20Encouraged%20by%20the%20positive%20response%2C%20the%20DMK%20is%20considering%20utilising%20similar%20AI-driven%20events%20closer%20to%20the%20elections.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20may%20employ%20AI-generated%20speeches%20of%20Jayalalitha%20to%20capitalise%20on%20her%20enduring%20charisma%20among%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20flipside%20to%20it%20too.%20A%20notable%20instance%20of%20AI%2Fdeepfake%20misuse%20occurred%20during%20the%20Telangana%20Assembly%20elections%20on%20November%2030%2C%202023%2C%20when%20a%20seven-second%20clip%20went%20viral%20on%20voting%20day.%20In%20the%20clip%2C%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi's%20(BRS)%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20was%20purportedly%20urging%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20their%20opponent%2C%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EMisuse%20Due%20To%20Loopholes%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20there%20is%20no%20specific%20legislation%20addressing%20AI%20and%20deep%20fake%20technology%20to%20penalise%20those%20responsible%20for%20creating%20them.%20The%20laws%20that%20could%20potentially%20apply%20if%20fake%20news%20is%20disseminated%20using%20deepfakes%20include%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%20(or%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%202023%20in%20the%20future)%3B%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%2C%202000%3B%20and%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20growing%20concerns%20that%20AI%20will%20be%20exploited%20to%20spread%20both%20true%20and%20false%20information%20during%20elections%20to%20sway%20public%20opinion.%20Experts%20warn%20that%20such%20misuse%20could%20distort%20the%20electoral%20process%20and%20undermine%20the%20democratic%20principles%20of%20transparency%20and%20fairness.%20AI's%20potential%20misuse%20includes%20the%20creation%20and%20dissemination%20of%20misinformation%2C%20such%20as%20fake%20news%20or%20manipulated%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPublic%20has%20to%20be%20made%20aware%20of%20AI%20as%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20population%20still%20doesn't%20know%20about%20this%20technology.%20People%20must%20fact-check%20before%20sharing%20any%20content%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mr%20Jadoun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20glitch%2C%C2%A0the%20Information%20Technology%20Ministry%20recently%20issued%20an%20advisory%20to%20generative%20AI%20companies%20like%20Google%20and%20OpenAI%20and%20also%20to%20others%20running%20such%20platforms.%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20with%20such%20diversity%2C%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20is%20all%20the%20more%20challenging.%20Deshpande%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20vast%20linguistic%20and%20dialectical%20diversity%20of%20India%20makes%20it%20exceedingly%20difficult%20for%20large%20digital%20platforms%20like%20Facebook%20and%20WhatsApp%20to%20effectively%20vet%20and%20control%20misleading%20content.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20challenge%20is%20not%20just%20the%20volume%20of%20the%20content%20but%20also%20its%20nuanced%20cultural%20and%20linguistic%20context%2C%20which%20requires%20sophisticated%C2%A0understanding%20and%20technology%20to%20address.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Use%20of%20AI%20In%20South%20Asian%20Elections%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20international%20legislation%20governing%20AI%20and%20its%20potential%20misuse%20raises%20significant%20concerns%20regarding%20its%20utilisation%20in%20elections%20worldwide.%20The%20year%202024%20presents%20an%20unprecedented%20scenario%2C%20with%20over%2050%20elections%20scheduled%20globally%2C%20encompassing%20approximately%204%20billion%20eligible%20voters.%20The%20United%20Nations%20has%20acknowledged%20the%20misuse%20of%20AI%20as%20a%20'global%20concern'.%20In%20the%20recently%20concluded%20general%20elections%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20world%20witnessed%20how%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan's%20party%2C%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%2C%20employed%20AI%20to%20replicate%20his%20voice%20in%20speeches%20while%20Khan%20himself%20was%20incarcerated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20during%20the%20Bangladesh%20elections%20in%20January%20of%20this%20year%2C%20opposition%20parties%20raised%20allegations%20of%20AI%20misuse%20by%20pro-government%20entities.%20These%20entities%20purportedly%20utilised%20deepfakes%20to%20target%20opposition%20factions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intricacies%20of%20AI%20tools%20render%20it%20exceedingly%20difficult%20to%20trace%20the%20perpetrators%20behind%20such%20malfeasance.%20This%20ambiguity%20poses%20the%20most%20concerning%20aspect%20of%20AI%2C%20as%20it%20blurs%20the%20lines%20between%20reality%20and%20falsehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cb%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709899740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Frmragapg_election-commission-reuters_625x300_05_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fais-impact-on-2024-lok-sabha-polls-are-we-prepared-5200770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20actively%20harnessing%20AI%20to%20enhance%20their%20campaign%20strategies.%20However%2C%20current%20assessments%20suggest%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20adopted%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20approach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fais-impact-on-2024-lok-sabha-polls-are-we-prepared-5200770%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fais-impact-on-2024-lok-sabha-polls-are-we-prepared-5200770%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fais-impact-on-2024-lok-sabha-polls-are-we-prepared-5200770%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Global%20Soft%20Power%20Index%3A%20India's%20Ranking%20Slips%20from%2028th%20to%2029th%20Position%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08160250%2FUntitled-design-34.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20ranking%20on%20the%20Global%20Soft%20Power%20Index%20has%20fallen%20to%2029th%20position%20from%20the%2028th%20position%20it%20had%20secured%20in%202023%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmoderndiplomacy.eu%2F2024%2F03%2F01%2Fglobal-soft-power-index-2024-usa-and-uk-ranked-top-nation-brands-china-takes-third-place%2F%5C%22%3E%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EModern%20Diplomacy%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp