0an%20elderly%20person%2C%20who%20has%20spent%20their%20life%20more%20in%20water%20queues%20than%20at%20home%20or%20the%20workplace%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20has%20witnessed%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20political%20planning%2C%20little%20actual%20implementation%2C%20and%20almost%20no%20fruitful%20outcomes%20with%20respect%20to%20water%20security.%20For%20years%20the%20thirsty%20city%20has%20swung%20between%20Cauvery%20and%20water%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegretfully%2C%20the%20tale%20is%20unchanged%20this%20year%20as%20well.%20The%20city%20receives%20around%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fbengaluru-water-shortage-crisis-water-tanker-prices-cauvery-river-summer-2506197-2024-02-23%5C%22%3E%201%2C450%20million%20litres%20per%20day%20(MLD)%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20water%20from%20the%20Cauvery%20but%20it%20faces%20a%20shortfall%20of%201%2C680%20million%20litres%20per%20day.%20%3Cspan%3EA%20tanker%20load%20(which%20are%20usually%20used%20as%20a%20source%20of%20water%20by%20the%20common%20public%20and%20commercial%20establishments%20as%20well)%20with%2012%2C000%20litre%20capacity%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Enow%20costs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fbengaluru%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-scarcity-worsens-tanker-prices-surge-up-to-rs-2850-2913143%5C%22%3ERs%201%2C500%20to%20Rs%202000%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20which%20was%20the%20rate%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20efforts%20made%20by%20Karnataka%20government%20%E2%80%94%20not%20enough%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20water%20is%20increasingly%20unavailable%20and%20unaffordable%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20under%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20strain%20and%20hence%20has%20proposed%20some%20urgent%20steps.%C2%A0%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fwater-crisis-in-bengaluru-government-assures-sufficient-supply-of-water%2Farticleshow%2F108248892.cms%3Futm_source%3Dcontentofinterest%26utm_medium%3Dtext%26utm_campaign%3Dcppst%5C%22%3Egovernment%20has%20ordered%20supply%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20water%20in%20huge%20tankers%20to%20Bengaluru%20from%20adjoining%20towns%20such%20as%20Ramanagara%2C%20Hoskote%2C%20Magadi%20and%20Channapatna%20and%20has%20planned%20to%20use%20milk%20tankers%20and%20take%20over%20private%20borewells%20to%20resolve%20the%20water%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20act%20on%20these%20plans%2C%20a%20substantial%20budget%20of%20Rs%20131%20crore%20is%20allotted%20by%20civil%20bodies%20for%20drilling%20borewells%20in%20priority%20zones.%20Simultaneously%2C%20to%20control%20water%20prices%2C%20all%20private%20water%20tankers%20and%20borewells%20are%20instructed%20to%20register%20with%20the%20Bangalore%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board%3Cem%3E%20(%3C%2Fem%3EBWSSB)%20before%20March%207%20to%20avoid%20facing%20seizures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20doubts%20regarding%20the%20strategies%20suggested%20to%20guarantee%20the%20availability%20of%20water%20since%203%2C700%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fbengaluru%2Fkarnataka-government-to-takeover-private-water-tankers-in-bengaluru-amid-severe-water-shortage-deputy-cm-2919285%5C%22%3Epublic%20borewells%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20city%20have%20significantly%20reduced%20the%20water%20levels%20and%201%2C214%20of%20the%2010%2C955%20borewells%20in%20the%20city%20have%20run%20dry%20%E2%80%94%20one%20could%20wonder%20how%20the%20financial%20help%20will%20be%20used%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20possible%20to%20think%20that%20some%20of%20the%20funds%20will%20be%20utilised%20to%20build%20water%20purification%20facilities%20and%20recycle%20spent%20water%2C%20however%2C%20specifics%20are%20still%20unknown.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20required%20details%20on%20the%20plan%20of%20action%2C%20the%20doubts%20would%20remain%2C%20mainly%20because%20such%20a%20plan%20of%20action%20is%20not%20the%20first%20initiative%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20even%20a%20policy%20called%20Karnataka%20Water%20Policy%202022%C2%A0had%20suggested%20strategies%20like%20re-cycling%2C%20re-use%20of%20treated%20waste%20water%20and%20rain%20water%20harvesting%2C%20industrial%20water%20use%20planning%20and%20other%20such%20measures.%20There%20have%20been%20not%20much%20noticeable%20changes%20on%20the%20ground%20level%20as%20people%20have%20to%20stand%20in%20queues%20and%20are%20bound%20to%20buy%20water%20at%20high%20prices%20even%20in%20March%2C%20when%20the%20summer%20months%20are%20just%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20question%20to%20reflect%20on%20is%20what%20has%20been%20compromised%20again%20and%20again%20and%20what%20is%20going%20wrong.%20Are%20the%20demands%20not%20being%20calculated%20in%20terms%20of%20water%20footnotes%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ewhich%20refers%20to%20%3Cspan%3Ehow%20much%20water%20is%20used%20for%20domestic%2C%20industrial%2C%20or%20agricultural%20or%20other%20purposes%3B%20it%20also%20means%2C%20how%20much%20water%20is%20available%20to%20use%20in%20the%20form%20of%20river%20and%20water%20bodies%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eor%20are%20the%20calculations%20wrong%20because%20of%20the%20increase%20in%20population%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20causes%20of%20the%20failures%20and%20problems%20related%20to%20water%20governance%20should%20be%20examined%20as%20a%20whole%20mainly%20because%20this%20is%20not%20a%20case%20of%20%E2%80%98tapless%20homes%E2%80%99%20but%20a%20problem%20of%20%E2%80%98waterless%20taps%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnplanned%20urbanisation%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20uncertain%20rains%20and%20changing%20climatic%20conditions%20cannot%20be%20blamed%20for%20the%20water%20crisis%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%C2%A0population%20explosion%2C%20unplanned%20urbanisation%2C%20unfriendly%20industrial%20and%20agricultural%20policies%20have%20also%20resulted%20in%20this%20problem.%20Unquestionably%2C%20water%20planning%20has%20not%20produced%20the%20desired%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BWSSB%2C%20which%20is%20primarily%20responsible%20for%20supplying%20the%20city%20with%20water%20has%20acknowledged%20that%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20water%20supply%20is%20becoming%20scarcer%20due%20to%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20excessive%20reliance%20on%20the%20Cauvery%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20co-ordinated%20water%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20conditions%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20envisage%20brighter%20times%20ahead%20because%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20expected%20to%20shoot%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fbengalurus-population-to-shoot-up-to-203-million-by-2031%2Farticle20941568.ece%5C%22%3E20.3%20million%20by%202031%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ewhich%20would%20once%20again%20throw%20the%20supply%20and%20demand%20gap%20for%20water%20off%20the%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BWSSB%20had%20previously%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20average%20annual%20population%20growth%20of%203%25%20over%20the%20next%2030%20years%20will%20mean%20that%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20future%20water%20demand%20cannot%20be%20met%20by%20the%20river%20Cauvery%20alone.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20wise%20water%20use%20is%20urgently%20needed%2C%20and%20moving%20towards%20effective%20water%20demand%20management%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BWSSB%20in%20a%20document%20titled%20%E2%80%9CBlueprint%20for%20the%20Future%E2%80%9D%20had%20suggested%20some%20innovative%20measures%20for%20water%20management%20like%20establishment%20of%20a%20forum%20called%20Water%20Future%20Hub.%20The%20water%20board%20envisaged%20that%20t%3Cspan%3Ehe%20hub%20would%20connect%20local%20companies%20with%20national%20and%20international%20experts%20to%20share%20knowledge%20and%20capabilities%20that%20can%20develop%20new%20ideas%2C%20innovative%20solutions%20to%20address%20future%20water%20challenges.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20BWSSB%20also%20proposed%20establishing%20a%20Water%20Centre%20to%20promote%20concepts%20like%20water%20conservation%2C%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20water%20reuse%20among%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20water%20is%20still%20far%20from%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20people%20in%20many%20areas%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20state%20capital.%20The%20water%20bodies%20are%20still%20polluted%20and%20the%20water%20conservation%20plans%20are%20still%20in%20the%20process%20without%20much%20success.%20Given%20that%20the%20pain%20experienced%20by%20those%20suffering%20from%20water%20poverty%20appears%20to%20be%20never-ending%2C%20an%20emphatic%20analysis%20of%20their%20circumstances%20is%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproaches%20towards%20water%20governance%20should%20be%20more%20human-centric%20rather%20than%20tech-centric.%20This%20can%20help%20common%20people%20understand%20what%20is%20happening%20with%20respect%20to%20water%20planning%20and%20who%20are%20the%20real%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20water%20projects.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20thirsty%20of%20the%20city%20cannot%20be%20a%20subject%20of%20politics%20and%20hence%20immediate%20effective%20steps%20are%20required%20to%20be%20taken%2C%20sensitively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EDr.%20Deepti%20Acharya%20is%20working%20as%20Senior%20Assistant%20Professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Political%20Science%2C%20The%20Maharaja%20Sayajirao%20University%20of%20Baroda%2C%20Vadodara%20and%20author%20of%20the%20Book%20Water%20and%20Public%20Polices%20in%20India%2C%20Routledge%2C%20New%20York%20and%20London%2C%202021.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709896547000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F07172944%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-07-at-5.28.39-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fbengalurus-water-crisis-whos-s