oject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fformer-british-pm-theresa-may-to-stand-down-at-next-election%2Famp_articleshow%2F108321467.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fformer-british-pm-theresa-may-to-stand-down-at-next-election%2Famp_articleshow%2F108321467.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Ranked%20104%2C%20Between%20Niger%20and%20Ivory%20Coast%2C%20on%20the%20Liberal%20Democracy%20Index%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124417%2Fsilence-1715729_1920.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20V-Dem%20(or%20Varieties%20of%20Democracy)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fv-dem.net%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20finds%20India%20to%20be%20in%20the%20bottom%2040-50%25%20of%20the%20179%20countries%20reviewed%2C%20and%20now%20situated%20between%20Niger%20(better)%20and%20Ivory%20Coast%20(worse).%20It%20calls%20out%20the%20sharp%20autocratisation%20in%20India%20from%202013%2C%20putting%20it%20at%20one%20of%20the%20top%20ten%20autocratisers%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20with%20pulling%20down%20democracy%20at%20levels%20as%20it%20was%20in%201975.%20India%20also%20accounts%20for%20%E2%80%9Cabout%20half%20of%20the%20population%20living%20in%20autocratising%20countries.%E2%80%9D%20It%20notes%20that%20India%20is%20no%20longer%20termed%20a%20democracy%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cdropped%20down%20to%20electoral%20autocracy%20in%202018%E2%80%9D%20and%20remains%20there%20at%20the%20end%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20observes%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwave%20of%20autocratisation%20is%20observable%20globally.%20Autocratisation%20is%20ongoing%20in%20%E2%80%9C42%20countries%2C%20home%20to%202.8%20billion%20people%2C%20or%2035%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population.%20India%2C%20with%2018%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20accounts%20for%20about%20half%20of%20the%20population%20living%20in%20autocratising%20countries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20level%20of%20liberal%20democracy%20enjoyed%20by%20the%20average%20human%20in%20the%20(South%20Asia)%20region%20is%20now%20down%20to%20levels%20last%20seen%20in%201975%20%E2%80%93%20almost%20half%20a%20century%20ago.%20That%20was%20when%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20ended%20and%20when%20Indira%20Gandhi%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%20The%20population-weighted%20index%20puts%20India%E2%80%99s%201.4%20billion%20citizens%20as%20being%20under%20autocracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20cites%20India%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20worst%20autocratisers%20lately.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComponent%20indices%20which%20add%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20V-Dem%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ELiberal%20Democracy%20Index%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(LDI)%20%E2%80%9Ccaptures%20both%20liberal%20and%20electoral%20aspects%20of%20democracy%20based%20on%20the%2071%20indicators%20included%20in%20the%20Liberal%20Component%20Index%20(LCI)%20and%20the%20Electoral%20Democracy%20Index%20(EDI).%E2%80%9D%20India%20is%20at%20rank%20104%2C%20with%20a%20score%20of%20.28%20on%20this%20count%20and%20this%20has%20worsened%20over%20last%20time.%20Pakistan%20for%20context%20is%20at%20119th%20rank%20and%20a%20score%20at%20.21%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20V-Dem%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EElectoral%20Democracy%20Index%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(EDI)%20%E2%80%9Ccaptures%20not%20only%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20regimes%20hold%20clean%2C%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%20but%20also%20their%20actual%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20alternative%20sources%20of%20information%20and%20association%2C%20as%20well%20as%20male%20and%20female%20suffrage%20and%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20government%20policy%20is%20vested%20in%20elected%20political%20officials.%E2%80%9D%20On%20this%20score%2C%20India%20is%20at%20rank%20110%20with%20its%20score%20having%20significantly%20worsened.%20The%20Report%20notes%20India%E2%80%99s%20worsening%20record%20here%20too%2C%20and%20speaking%20globally%2C%20it%20finds%20that%20the%20Clean%20Elections%20Index%20%E2%80%9Cappear%20on%20the%20top%2020%20list%20of%20aspects%20that%20are%20undermined%20in%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20autocratising%20countries.%20The%20indicator%20for%20free%20and%20fairness%20of%20elections%20deteriorated%20substantially%20and%20significantly%20in%2018%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20EU-member%20Hungary%2C%20the%20most%20populous%20country%20in%20the%20world%20India%2C%20and%20The%20Philippines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20453px)%2085vw%2C%20453px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124051%2FScreenshot-2024-03-08-at-12.40.31-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22453%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124051%2FScreenshot-2024-03-08-at-12.40.31-PM.png%20751w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124051%2FScreenshot-2024-03-08-at-12.40.31-PM-188x300.png%20188w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124051%2FScreenshot-2024-03-08-at-12.40.31-PM-641x1024.png%20641w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700744%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20V-Dem%20report%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ELiberal%20Component%20Index%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20where%20the%20%E2%80%9Cliberal%20principle%20of%20democracy%E2%80%9D%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20captures%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20importance%20of%20protecting%20individual%20and%20minority%20rights%20against%20both%20the%20tyranny%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20tyranny%20of%20the%20majority.%20It%20also%20captures%20the%20%E2%80%9Chorizontal%E2%80%9D%20methods%20of%20accountability%20between%20more%20or%20less%20equally%20standing%20institutions%20that%20ensure%20the%20effective%20checks%20and%20balances%20between%20institutions%20and%20in%20particular%20limit%20the%20exercise%20of%20executive%20power.%E2%80%9D%20Here%2C%20India%20has%20been%20ranked%20at%2092%2C%20but%20again%2C%20scores%20have%20fallen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EEgalitarian%20Component%20Index%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Cmeasures%20to%20what%20extent%20all%20social%20groups%20enjoy%20equal%20capabilities%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20political%20arena%E2%80%9D%20is%20where%20India%20finds%20its%20lowest%20rank%2C%20in%20the%20bottom%2045%20countries%2C%20at%20137.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EParticipatory%20Component%20Index%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20views%20active%20participation%20by%20citizens%20in%20all%20political%20processes%20as%20favourable%2C%20India%20ranks%20at%20103%2C%20with%20significant%20deterioration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20V-Dem%20Deliberative%20Component%20Index%20(DCI)%20looking%20to%20capture%20to%20what%20extent%20the%20deliberative%20principle%20of%20democracy%20is%20achieved%2C%20it%20assesses%20the%20process%20by%20which%20decisions%20are%20reached%20in%20a%20polity.%20A%20deliberative%20process%20is%20one%20in%20which%20public%20reasoning%2C%20focused%20on%20the%20common%20good%2C%20motivates%20political%20decisions%20%E2%80%93%20as%20contrasted%20with%20emotional%20appeals%2C%20solidary%20attachments%2C%20parochial%20interests%20or%20coercion.%E2%80%9D%20Here%20India%20ranks%20at%20101%2C%20again%20with%20a%20deterioration%20in%20the%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegionally%20speaking%3A%20Bhutan%20only%20liberal%20democracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20finds%20%E2%80%9CSouth%20and%20Central%20Asia%20is%20now%20the%20second%20most%20autocratic%20region%20in%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%20More%20than%20nine%20out%20of%20ten%20people%2C%20or%2093%25%20of%20the%20population%20reside%20in%20electoral%20autocracies%20like%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Kazakhstan.%20Afghanistan%2C%20Turkmenistan%2C%20and%20Uzbekistan%20are%20closed%20autocracies%2C%20accounting%20for%204%25%20of%20the%20regional%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20mere%203%25%20reside%20in%20electoral%20democracies%2C%20including%20countries%20like%20Armenia%2C%20and%20Georgia%2C%20while%20only%20one%20country%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20is%20a%20liberal%20democracy.%20In%202023%2C%20only%20Mongolia%20descended%20from%20an%20electoral%20democracy%20regime%20type%20to%20the%20democratic%20%E2%80%9Cgrey%20zone%E2%80%9D%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHandling%20of%20dissent%20and%20digital%20repression%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cprocess%20of%20autocratisation%E2%80%9D%2C%20notes%20the%20V-Dem%20report%2C%20begins%20in%20earnest%20from%202008%20and%20characteristically%20proceeded%20in%20the%20incremental%2C%20slow-moving%20fashion%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cthird%20wave%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20autocratisation%20process%20has%20been%20well%20documented%2C%20including%20gradual%20but%20substantial%20deterioration%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20compromising%20independence%20of%20the%20media%2C%20crackdowns%20on%20social%20media%2C%20harassments%20of%20journalists%20critical%20of%20the%20government%2C%20as%20well%20as%20attacks%20on%20civil%20society%20and%20intimidation%20of%20the%20opposition.%20The%20ruling%20anti-pluralist%2C%20Hindu-nationalist%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20at%20the%20helm%20has%20for%20example%20used%20laws%20on%20sedition%2C%20defamation%2C%20and%20counterterrorism%20to%20silence%20critics.%20The%20BJP%20government%20undermined%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20secularism%20by%20amending%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20in%202019.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20cites%20India%E2%80%99s%20shrinking%20environment%20for%20religious%20freedoms.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Modi-led%20government%20also%20continues%20to%20suppress%20the%20freedom%20of%20religion%20rights.%20Intimidation%20of%20political%20opponents%20and%20people%20protesting%20government%20policies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20silencing%20of%20dissent%20in%20academia%20are%20now%20prevalent.%20India%20dropped%20down%20to%20electoral%20autocracy%20in%202018%20and%20remains%20in%20this%20category%20by%20the%20end%20of%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20so%20far%20as%20media%20impacts%20on%20ensuring%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20and%20dissemination%20of%20good%20information%20to%20enable%20the%20making%20of%20choices%20and%20a%20robust%20civil%20society%2C%20the%20report%20singles%20out%20El%20Salvador%2C%20India%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnotably%20Mauritius%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Camong%20the%20worst%20government%20offenders%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20increasing%20their%20efforts%20to%20censor%20the%20media.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20sees%2014%20countries%20seeing%20a%20significant%20decline%20over%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20on%20the%20indicator%20for%20internet%20freedoms.%20India%20finds%20itself%20in%20the%20company%20of%20%E2%80%9CBelarus%2C%20Eswatini%2C%20Guinea%2C%20Iran%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20Sudan%E2%80%9D%20which%20indicate%20that%20in%202023%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthese%20governments%20shut%20down%20the%20internet%20multiple%20times%20during%20the%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20noted%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia-internet-shutdown-capital-of-the-world%2Fa-64997062%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520a%2520recent%2520report%2Cthan%2520in%2520any%2520other%2520country.%5C%22%3EInternet%20Shutdown%20Capital%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20continuously%2C%20by%20other%20indices%20and%20criticised%20for%20it.%20It%20accounted%20for%2058%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20shutdowns%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20media%20control%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Guinea%2C%20Nicaragua%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20Russia%20are%20all%20countries%20with%20scores%20higher%20than%202%20for%202023%2C%20on%20an%20index%20to%20calculate%20the%20ability%20of%20governments%20to%20control%20social%20media.%20This%20score%20of%20%E2%80%9Chigher%20than%202%2C%E2%80%9D%20indicates%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20successful%20censorship%20of%20most%20targeted%20political%20content%20on%20social%20media.%E2%80%9D%20Here%20too%2C%20India%20is%20with%20%E2%80%9CBelarus%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Kyrgyzstan%2C%20Montenegro%2C%20Tanzania%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20Yemen%E2%80%9D%20where%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20media%20content%20has%20been%20increasingly%20controlled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20recently%20as%20in%20the%20farmers%20protest%20and%20attempts%20to%20march%20to%20Delhi%2C%20there%20were%20reports%20on%20ordering%20social%20media%20to%20take%20down%20farmer%20or%20supporter%20accounts.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68366859%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20X%20spoke%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20orders%20and%20X%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdisagreement%E2%80%9D%20with%20them%2C%20but%20compliance.%20A%20story%20on%20alleged%20torture%20and%20deaths%20of%20civilians%20in%20Poonch%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20by%20the%20Army%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fcrime%2Findian-army-torture-jammu-and-kashmir-poonch-bjp-gujjar-bakkerwal%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20pulled%20on%20government%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Most%20populous%20country%E2%80%99%20autocratising%20impacts%20global%20stats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20population%20makes%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20autocratisation%20look%20very%20stark%20if%20evaluated%20per%20citizen%20living%20under%20an%20autocratic%20regime%2C%20almost%20a%20Vishwaguru%20of%20autocratisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20commentary%20on%20the%20Democracy%20Report%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%202012%20to%202022%2C%20the%20mean%20Electoral%20Democracy%20index%20score%20fell%20by%200.03%2C%20from%200.53%20to%200.50%2C%20when%20weighting%20all%20countries%20equally.%20Weighted%20by%20population%2C%20however%2C%20it%20fell%20by%200.13%20points%2C%20from%200.54%20to%200.41.%20Weighed%20by%20population%2C%20but%20excluding%20India%2C%20it%20fell%20only%200.05%2C%20from%200.46%20to%200.41.%20Hence%2C%20developments%20in%20India%20drive%20many%20of%20the%20most%20dramatic%20developments%20depicted%20in%20different%20Democracy%20Report%20figures.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124225%2FScreenshot-2024-03-08-at-12.42.12-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124225%2FScreenshot-2024-03-08-at-12.42.12-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124225%2FScreenshot-2024-03-08-at-12.42.12-PM-300x200.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08124225%2FScreenshot-2024-03-08-at-12.42.12-PM-1024x678.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700745%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22795%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20V-Dem%20report%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20rise%20by%2048%25%20of%20those%20living%20under%20autocracies.%20Also%2C%20%E2%80%9C44%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20or%203.5%20billion%20people%20%E2%80%93%20resi