their%20award-winning%20documentary%20titled%20%E2%80%98Coral%20Woman%E2%80%99%20was%20released%2C%20featuring%20Uma%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20the%20damage%20being%20caused%20to%20marine%20life.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20we%20do%20not%20talk%20about%20the%20coral%20reefs%2C%20so%20this%20film%20was%20an%20eye-opener%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Uma%20hosted%20several%20painting%20exhibitions%20across%20the%20country%20to%20draw%20interest%20to%20the%20subject.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20coral%20reefs%20in%20my%20paintings%20are%20not%20happy%20anymore.%20Today%2C%20I%20depict%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20ocean%20on%20my%20canvas%20and%20paint%20their%20sufferings.%20I%20believe%20art%20is%20a%20very%20powerful%20medium%20to%20bring%20about%20social%20transformation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20decade%20since%20her%20first%20dive%2C%20but%20Uma%20continues%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20marine%20pollution%20in%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20corporate%20organisations.%20Recently%2C%20she%20was%20named%20the%20%E2%80%98Earth%20Champion%20of%20the%20Month%E2%80%99%20by%20Sony%20BBC%20Earth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPersonally%2C%20the%20transformation%20from%20being%20a%20homemaker%20to%20a%20scuba%20diver%20has%20given%20me%20an%20immense%20sense%20of%20responsibility.%20The%20oceans%20do%20not%20have%20a%20voice.%20I%20am%20one%20of%20the%20few%20who%20could%20communicate%20the%20reality.%20My%20work%20is%20small%20and%20it%20will%20take%20an%20entire%20village%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20change.%20We%20do%20not%20just%20need%20to%20talk%20the%20talk%20but%20walk%20the%20walk%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Uma%20Mani)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709736705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fcoral-woman-1-1709730480