20through%20an%20existential%20crisis%2C%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20What%20was%20the%20purpose%20of%20my%20life%3F%20I%20was%20depressed%2C%20alone%2C%20without%20a%20clear%20trajectory%20of%20life.%20My%20mother%20asked%20me%20to%20visit%20a%20temple%20as%20she%20felt%20it%20would%20make%20me%20happy.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Pinky%2C%20too%2C%20was%20going%20through%20a%20tough%20time%20and%20asked%20me%20if%20we%20could%20do%20something%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Poonam%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20highlighted%20above%2C%20she%20found%20her%20answer%20at%20the%20temple%20that%20changed%20her%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20tonnes%20of%20flowers%20were%20being%20dumped%20into%20the%20river%20daily.%20I%20found%20a%20company%20that%20was%20recycling%20flowers%20and%20asked%20for%20their%20help.%20They%20asked%20for%20my%20profile%20and%20said%20that%20they%20would%20let%20me%20know%20if%20they%20deemed%20it%20fit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20reply%20fuelled%20Poonam%E2%80%99s%20desire%20further%20and%20cemented%20her%20desire%20to%20look%20for%20solutions%20of%20her%20own.%20She%20was%20no%20longer%20going%20to%20let%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20opinions%20define%20her%20self-worth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20looked%20for%20what%20she%20could%20make%20with%20recycled%20floral%20waste%2C%20she%20came%20across%20a%20small%20business%20near%20her%20house%20who%20used%20cow%20dung%20powder%20to%20make%20incense%20sticks.%20Could%20she%20do%C2%A0the%20same%20with%20flowers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20small%20space%20provided%20by%20her%20brother%2C%20Poonam%20set%20up%20her%20unit.%20From%20June%202019%2C%20she%20will%20get%20up%20at%205%20am%20and%20go%20to%20temples%20near%20her%20residence.%20There%2C%20she%20would%20request%20the%20staff%20to%20give%20her%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20obliged%2C%20but%20they%20were%20also%20mixed%20with%20other%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201242px)%20100vw%2C%201242px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Poonam%20sells%20her%20products%20through%20exhibitions%20and%20her%20website%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913.jpeg%201242w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-300x199.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-500x331.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-768x509.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-150x99.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22823%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPoonam%20sells%20her%20products%20through%20exhibitions%20and%20her%20website.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%209%20am%2C%20she%20brought%20all%20the%20waste%20in%20her%20car%2C%20segregated%20it%20and%20dried%20it%20under%20the%20sun.%20In%20hopes%20of%20being%20able%20to%20experiment%20with%20these%20dried%20flowers%2C%20she%20faced%20her%20first%20hurdle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20drying%20the%20flowers%20for%20almost%20two%20months%2C%20I%20was%20going%20to%20powder%20them.%20I%20even%20bought%20a%20pulverizer%20machine%2C%20but%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20factor%20in%20the%20weather%2C%20and%20the%20flowers%20got%20drenched%20in%20the%20rainfall.%20All%20my%20flowers%20were%20spoiled%20and%20I%20had%20to%20start%20all%20over%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Poonam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20one%20to%20give%20up%2C%20she%20visited%20many%20temples%20again%2C%20and%20repeated%20the%20whole%20process.%20This%20time%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20successfully%20dry%20and%20powder%20the%20flowers.%20Using%20these%20powdered%20flowers%2C%20ghee%2C%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98havan%E2%80%99%20products%2C%20and%20other%20ingredients%2C%20she%20tried%20her%20hand%20at%20making%20dhoop%20sticks.%20Through%20some%20permutations%20and%20combinations%2C%20and%20hours%20of%20working%2C%20she%20found%20the%20winning%20combination%20of%2016%20herbs%20sometime%20in%20September%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20Janmashtami%202019.%20I%20took%20these%20dhoop%20sticks%20and%20gave%20them%20to%20the%20temple%20priest%20who%20supported%20me.%20He%20was%20so%20happy%20and%20promised%20to%20give%20me%20segregated%20floral%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%20entrepreneur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20initially%20invested%20her%20savings%20into%20the%20business%2C%20Poonam%20also%20took%20a%20Mudra%20loan%20to%20support%20her%20venture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claims%20that%20her%20products%20are%20organic%20and%20made%20with%20almost%2080%20percent%20floral%20waste.%20Unlike%20other%20incense%20and%20dhoop%20sticks%2C%20Aaruhi%20products%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20charcoal%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%203%2C000%20%E2%80%98Flower%20Recyclers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201242px)%20100vw%2C%201242px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Poonam%20has%20trained%20over%203000%20women%20in%20flower%20recycling%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365.jpeg%201242w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365-300x296.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365-500x494.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365-768x758.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365-96x96.jpeg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam2-min-1709639365-150x148.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343950%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221226%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPoonam%20has%20trained%20over%203%2C000%20women%20in%20flower%20recycling.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20the%20first%20step%20was%20sorted%2C%20the%20next%20step%20was%20selling%20it.%20But%20where%20would%20she%20sell%20it%3F%20She%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20a%20stall%20at%20Dilli%20Haat%20and%20at%20other%20exhibitions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20response%20was%20really%20good%20at%20the%20first%20stall%20I%20set%20up%20at%20Dilli%20Haat.%20Some%20teachers%20visited%20one%20of%20the%20exhibitions%20and%20wished%20to%20see%20my%20factory.%20Post%20that%2C%20they%20invited%20me%20to%20speak%20to%20their%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Poonam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20things%20started%20looking%20up%2C%20she%20was%20hit%20by%20another%20roadblock%20%E2%80%93%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20With%20the%20entire%20country%20shut%2C%20there%20were%20no%20exhibitions%20too.%20Poonam%20decided%20to%20turn%20this%20into%20an%20opportunity.%20She%20started%20selling%20her%20products%20online%20through%20her%20website%2C%20Whatsapp%20and%20Facebook.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20one%20door%20shuts%2C%20another%20one%20opens.%20Along%20with%20creating%20an%20online%20presence%2C%20I%20also%20worked%20on%20building%20a%20space%20through%20which%20I%20deliver%20talks%20and%20conduct%20skill-based%20programmes%20to%20generate%20a%20livelihood%20for%20underprivileged%20women.%20It%20is%20called%20the%20Save%20Prithvi%20Foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20is%20now%20a%20master%20trainer%20at%20Khadi%20India%2C%20National%20Cooperative%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20and%20has%20conducted%20training%20programmes%20with%20many%20government%20organisations%20like%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendras%20in%20Jammu%2C%20the%20rural%20development%20programme%20and%20more.%20She%20has%20trained%20over%203%2C000%20women%20and%20showed%20them%20a%20way%20to%20become%20self-reliant%2C%20while%20helping%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20collects%20floral%20waste%20from%20over%2015%20temples%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20today%20and%20gets%20almost%20100%20kg%20of%20waste%20every%20three%20days.%20Besides%20dhoop%2C%20which%20is%20her%20bestseller%2C%20she%20makes%20idols%20and%20air%20fresheners.%20Her%20products%20range%20from%20Rs%2050-350%2C%20earning%20her%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20Her%20dhoop%20stand%20and%20packaging%20too%2C%20is%20made%20from%20waste.%20She%20employs%205%20women%20at%20her%20unit%2C%20who%20she%20calls%20the%20%E2%80%98flower%20recyclers%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Poonam%2C%20this%20business%20helped%20her%20build%20her%20identity%20and%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20environment%20and%20lives%20of%20countless%20women.%20Her%20dream%20is%20to%20make%20India%20a%20country%20where%20not%20even%20one%20religious%20place%20throws%20flowers%20in%20the%20garbage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20all%20women%20like%20her%2C%20looking%20to%20fulfil%20their%20dream%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20get%20one%20opportunity%20in%20life%20to%20carve%20a%20path%20for%20ourselves.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20miss%20it.%20Live%20for%20yourself%20and%20do%20what%20makes%20you%20happy.%20The%20first%20step%20is%20always%20difficult%2C%20but%20once%20you%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20it%2C%20there%20is%20no%20looking%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAaruhi%20Enterprise%20products%20will%20soon%20be%20available%20on%20Amazon%20and%20Flipkart.%20You%20can%20also%20purchase%20them%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saveprithvi.com%2Fcategory%2Forganic-dhoop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Poonam%20Singh)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709706273000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fpoonam5-1709639330.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343922%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Poonam%20Singh%20started%20Aaruhi%20Enterprises%20to%20recycle%20floral%20waste%20from%20temples%20into%20incense%20sticks%20and%20more.%20She%20recycles%201%2C000%20kg%20waste%20per%20month%20and%20has%20upskilled%20over%203%2C000%20women%20so%20far%20with%20her%20awareness%20workshops.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343922%2Ftemple-flower-waste-recycling-startup-homemaker-turned-entrepreneur-incense-sticks-gurugram-poonam-singh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gas%20Industry%20Loses%20Bid%20To%20Block%20Green%20Building%20Codes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Gas%20companies%20and%20furnace%20manufacturers%20have%20on